\ip God…®n Akam Inigha Izir Gumazim Daniel…®n Ak…®nafarim a 6plan eghaghaniba ko 4plan irebabar akaba an iti. Me ak…®nafarir kam Judaba os…®mt…®ziba sara itir dughiam…®n an osiri, ez…® ak…®nafarir kam men n…®ghn…®zir gavgaviba gavgavim me dan…®ngasa. Kar men akurvaght…® me kamagh…®n fogh suam, God gumazamizir bar deragha an pozibar akurvasi. Eght…® g…®n God men os…®mt…®ziba g…®vagh dabirabir aghuim me dan…®ngam.
\ip Daniel…®n ak…®nafarim, akuar pumuning iti.
\ip 1. Sapta 1--6. Kar Daniel ko an namakabar eghaghaniba. Dughiar av…®ribar apaniba paz…® me damuasa, ez…® kamagh…®n me pamten n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n ikia egha arazir aghuibagh ami, ez…® apaniba me damuamin bizim me ibura.
\ip 2. Sapta 7--12. Kar Daniel ganizir irebaba. Dughiar kam…®n, God g…®fozir puvat…®zir gumazamizibar kantriba bar gavgavigha iti. Eght…® me ti God…®n gumazamiziba bar me ag…®vagham. Ez…® irebar kaba kamagh…®n men akakasi, God uan gumazamizibar akuragh, egh kantrin kabar gavgaviba ag…®vagham. Eght…® g…®n God…®n gumazamiziba bar deraghv…®ra ikiam.
\c 1
\ms1 Daniel uan namakaba ko men eghaghanim
\mr (Sapta 1--6)
\s1 Judan gumazir igiar maba atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n iti
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt 2 Atriviba 24:1; 2 Eghaghaniba 36:5-7\x*Fom…®ra Jehoiakim Judabar atrivim…®n itima, azenir pumuning ko m…®kezim g…®vaz…®ma, Babilon…®n kantrin Atrivim Nebukatnesar, a iz…® Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam ko m…®soghasa, egha an m…®dorozir gumaziba nguibam bar an ek…®aru.
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2-4 \xt 2 Atriviba 20:17-18; 24:10-16; 2 Eghaghaniba 36:10; Aisaia 29:7-8\x*Ez…® Ekiam Nebukatnesar amamangat…®z…®ma, an Atrivim Jehoiakim inigha Judan gumazamizir av…®rim inigha God…®n D…®penim…®n kav…®n aghuiba ko itariba ini. Egha da inigha Babilon…®n kantrin ghua uan asebar d…®penim…®n ghu. Egha bizir aghuir kaba isa d…®penir kam…®n aven itir danganir mogomem…®n da at…®.
\p 
\v 3 Ez…® Atrivim Nebukatnesar Judabar tong…®n gumazir igiar maba iniasa, uan d…®penim…®n ingarir gumazibar faragha zuir gumazim, Aspenas m…®gei. A ghaze, n…® Atrivim Jehoiakim…®n anabamra gan…®va gumazir igiabara iniva egh uaghan gumazir ekiabar adarazir otaritaba sara inigh.
\v 4 Egh a kamagh…®n garir gumazir igiaba iniam: me guar aghuiba ik…®va, namnar aghuiba ik…®va, egh tav m…®karzir tam ikuvighan kogh, egh fofozir av…®riba ik…®va, suren aghuibar amuva, uaghan zuam…®ra fofozim inigham. Eght…® me atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n ingaramin fofozim ikiam. Egh Aspenas uab…® men sure damut…® me Babilon…®n akam osir…®va egh a d…®ponam.
\v 5 Egha atrivim uaghan kamagh…®n m…®gei, dughiaba bar dagher me apiba ko wain…®n d…®par me apiba, me atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n itir gumazibar m…®n dar amam. Egh me azenir pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n sure damigh…®va g…®n me atrivim…®n ingangarir gumazibar otivam.
\p 
\v 6 Men tong…®n m…®sevezir gumazibar ziabar kara: Daniel, ko Hanania, ko Misael, ko Asaria, me bar Judan anabam…®n gumazir igiaba.
\v 7 Egha Aspenas ziar igiaba me gar…®ki. Daniel a Beltesasar a gat…®, egha Hanania a Satrak a gat…®, egha Misael a Mesak a gat…®, egha Asaria an Abetnego a gat…®.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Esekiel 4:13; Hosea 9:3\x*Ez…® Daniel dagheba ko wain…®n d…®paba ko bizir me atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n isa me gan…®diba, ana dar aman aghua. A pamten kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, a dagheba ko wain…®n d…®pam amegh, God…®n damazim…®n m…®zegham.\f + \fr 1:8 \ft Daniel…®n n…®ghn…®zim…®n m…®ngarim, a deragha bigha m…®geir puvat…®. Guizbang…®ra, Babilonia bizir guar av…®rir God Israelian anogorogheziba me dapi. Ez…® Israelian Araziba, wain…®n d…®pabar amasa men t…®vazir puvat…®. Babilonia ti dagheba uan aseba ofabar m…®n dagh an…®di, ez…® bizir kabar Daniel daman aghua. O a ti ghaze, an atrivim…®n dagher aghuiba iniam, egh arazir kam…®n an atrivim kamagh…®n an akagha ghaze, a bar atrivim an…®ngizir akabar g…®n mangam.\f* Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a uab…®n akurvaghasa Aspenas…®n azangs…®si, eght…® me dagher igharazitam a dan…®ngam.
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Jenesis 39:21\x*Ez…® God Aspenas gamima a Daniel…®n apangkuvigha an akurvaghasa.
\v 10 Egha Aspenas kamagh…®n Daniel m…®gei, вАЬK…® uan ekiam…®n atiatingi. K…® fo, a ia bagha dagheba ko d…®paba am…®sevegha g…®fa. Eght…® ia m…®karziba suegh aghariba guigh, egh ia, ia ko izezir gumazibar m…®n ganan koght…®ma, a na m…®sueght…® k…® aremegham.вАЭ
\p 
\v 11 Aspenas faragha Daniel, Hanania, Misael, ko Asaria, men ganasa gumazir mam am…®sefe. Ez…® Daniel ghua gumazir men garim kamagh…®n a m…®gei,
\v 12 вАЬN…® kamagh…®n e damu ganigh, n…® azenibar oparir dagheba ko d…®pamra, da e dan…®ng mang…® 10plan dughiabar tugh.
\v 13 Egh 10plan dughiar kabar g…®n, n…® gumazir igiar atrivim…®n dagheba apibar gan…®va, egh n…® en gan. Egh n…® fogham, en m…®karziba men m…®karzibar m…®n derav…®ram oto, o puvat…®? Egh n…® g…®n bizir tizim…®n e damus…®, n…® puram e damu.вАЭ
\v 14 Ez…® gumazir men garim, a Daniel…®n akam…®n g…®n ghua Daniel m…®kemez…® mogh…®n ami.
\p 
\v 15 Ez…® 10plan dughiabar g…®n, men ganganim bar deragha, men m…®karziba saram aghua gavgavigha, gumazir igiar atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n amezibagh afira.
\v 16 Ez…® gumazir men garim, an atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n dagheba ko wain…®n d…®paba isa zurara munagh da ar…®si. Egha azenibar oparir daghebara me gan…®gav…®ra iti.
\p 
\v 17 Ez…® 4plan gumazir igiar kaba, God biziba bar dar amuamin fofozim ko, ak…®nafaribar gara dagh fozir fofozir aghuim, ko n…®ghn…®zir aghuim me gan…®ngi. Egha God Daniel fofozim a gan…®ngiz…®ma, a irebaba ko irebam…®n m…®n garir bizibar m…®ngaribar gun m…®k…®mamin fofozim ti.
\p 
\v 18 Ez…® Judan gumazir igiar kaba bar, me azenir pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n sure ag…®fa, dughiar Atrivim Nebukatnesar inabazim. Ez…® Aspenas me inigha atrivim bagha ghu.
\v 19 Ez…® atrivim me ko m…®g…®ava kamagh…®n gari, Daniel, Hanania, Misael, ko Asaria, men fofozim gumazir igiar mabar fofozibagh afira. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a me iniz…®ma me an ingangarir gumazibar otifi.
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt 1 Atriviba 10:1\x*Egha atrivim bizir av…®ribar men azangs…®gha, me ko m…®g…®a gari, men fofozim Babilon…®n fofozir gumazibar fofoziba, bar mogh…®ra me gafira. Atrivim…®n irebar m…®ngaribagh fogha dar gun m…®geir gumaziba ko, kukunir gumaziba bar, me Judan gumazir 4plan kabagh afiraghan kogham. Bar puvat…®.
\p 
\v 21 Egha Daniel dughiar ruarim…®n atrivim…®n ingangarim gami. Egha a ingara ikiav…®ra itima, Sairus Babilon…®n atrivim…®n oto.
\c 2
\s1 Nebukatnesar…®n irebam
\p 
\v 1 Nebukatnesar azenir pumuning uan kantrin garava an atrivim…®n iti. Egha d…®magarir mam, a irebam…®n gani. Ez…® irebar kam a gamima a bar osemegha akuava avenge.
\v 2 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, irebar m…®ngaribagh fogha dar gun m…®geir gumaziba ko, kukunir gumaziba ko, imezibagh amir gumaziba ko, akavsiar ifavaribagh amir gumaziba, me bagha akam amada. Eght…® me iz…® an irebam…®n m…®ngarim…®n gun m…®k…®mam. Egha me iza atrivim…®n guam…®n tuiviz…®,
\v 3 a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, вАЬK…® irebam…®n ganiz…®, irebar kam na gamima nan navim bar oseme. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® irebam…®n m…®ngarim g…®foghasa.вАЭ
\p 
\v 4 Egha me kamagh…®n Aram…®n akam…®n atrivim…®n akam ikaragha ghaze, вАЬAtrivim,\f + \fr 2:4 \ft Akar kagh ikegha ghua Daniel 7:28…®n tuziba, me Hibrun akam…®n dar osirizir puvat…®. Me Aram…®n akam…®n an osiri.\f* n…® bar deraghv…®ra ik…® mamagh…®ra ik…®. E ghaze, n…® faragh uan irebam…®n e m…®kemeght…®, e an m…®ngarim…®n gun n…® m…®k…®mam.вАЭ
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n gumazir kabav g…®a ghaze, вАЬK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, ia bizir k…® irebam…®n ganizibar gun na m…®kemeghan kogh, egh uaghan an m…®ngarim…®n gun m…®kemeghan koght…®, k…® m…®dorozir gumazibav kemeght…®, me ian sueba ko aghariba asight…®, ia aremegham. Egh me ian d…®penibagh as…®ghas…®gh…®va, dar amut…® da bar ikuvigham.
\v 6 Egh ia v…®rara irebam ko an m…®ngarim sara na m…®kemeght…®, k…® bizir av…®rim ia dan…®ng, egh ia damut…® ia ziar ekiam iniam. Kamagh…®n dat…®r…®gh…®n, ia irebam ko an m…®ngarim…®n gun na m…®k…®m.вАЭ
\p 
\v 7 Egha me uam atrivim m…®gei, вАЬN…® irebar kam…®n gun e m…®kemeght…®, e an m…®ngarim…®n gun n…® m…®k…®mam.вАЭ
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n m…®gei, вАЬK…® ian ifavaribagh fogha g…®fa. Ia dughiar ruarim m…®zuamasa, kamagh…®n ia ghaze, k…® akam otavk…®ri. Ez…® bar puvat…®.
\v 9 Guizbang…®ra, ia bizir k…® irebam…®n ganizibar gun na m…®kemeghan kogh…®va, ia bar os…®mt…®zir magh gariba iniam. K…® fo, ia bar navir vam…®ra inigha ghaze, ia na gifar mang…®t…® k…® uan n…®ghn…®zim otevk…®nigham. Kamagh…®n, ia irebar kam…®n gun na m…®k…®m, eght…® k…® fogham, ia uaghan an m…®ngarim sara na m…®kemegh.вАЭ
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® fofozir gumazir kaba atrivim…®n akam baregha, kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, вАЬAtrivim, nguazir kam…®n gumazitam bizir n…® damuasa e m…®kemezim damighan kogham. Bar puvat…®. Atrivim, atrivir gavgavir ekiatam, uan irebar m…®ngaribagh fogha dar gun m…®geir gumazitam, ko kukunir gumazitam, ko akavsiar ifavaribagh amir gumazitam, an azangs…®zir katam…®n a gamizir puvat…®.
\v 11 \x - \xo 2:11 \xt Jenesis 41:39; Aisaia 57:15; Daniel 5:11\x*Atrivim, bizir n…® en azangs…®ziba, e dav k…®man ibura. Ez…® gumazitam dar amighan kogham. Aseba dar amuam. Egha aser kaba da gumaziba ko itir puvat…®.вАЭ
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® atrivim akar kam baregha bar puv…®ram atari. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a m…®dorozir gumaziba bagha akam amadagha ghaze, me Babilon…®n fofozir gumaziba bar me m…®sueght…®ma me aremegham.
\v 13 Ez…® m…®dorozir gumaziba ghua, Daniel uan namakaba ko me m…®sueght…® me aremeghasa me buriagha arui.
\s1 God irebam…®n m…®ngarim Daniel…®n aka
\p 
\v 14 Ez…® atrivim…®n m…®dorozir gumazibar garir gumazim Ariok, d…®kavigha Babilon…®n fofozir gumazibav sueght…® me aremeghasa zui. Ez…® Daniel a m…®k…®masa derav…®ra n…®ghnigha,
\v 15 kamagh…®n Ariok…®n azara, вАЬManmaghsua, atrivim fofozir gumazibav sueght…® me aremeghasa m…®g…®r…®g…®ar gavgavir kam gami?вАЭ Ez…® Ariok bizir otivizir kabar gun a m…®gei.
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® Daniel fofozir gumaziba aremeghan aghuagha, zuam…®ra ghua atrivim…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, вАЬN…® tong dughiam na danight…® k…® irebam…®n m…®ngarim…®n gun m…®k…®mam.вАЭ
\p 
\v 17 Ez…® atrivim akar kam amamangat…®z…®, Daniel uamategha uan d…®penim…®n ghugha uan namakaba, Hanania, Misael, ko Asaria, bizir otiviziba bar dar gun me m…®keme.
\v 18 Egha apangkuvim bagha God…®n Uan Nguibam…®n Itim ko m…®k…®masa me m…®gei. Egh uaghan irebar mogomem…®n itim bagh azangs…®ght…®, an an m…®ngarim en akagham. Eght…® e Babilon…®n fofozir gumazir igharaziba ko aremeghan kogham.
\v 19 Ez…® d…®magarir kamra God, atrivim…®n irebam…®n m…®ngarim Daniel…®n aka. Ez…® Daniel God…®n Uan Nguibam…®n Itim…®n ziam fa,
\v 20 egha kamagh…®n m…®gei:
\b
\q1 вАЬGod, k…® n…®n ziam f…® mamagh…®ra ikiam.
\q2 Guizbang…®ra, fofoziba ko gavgaviba bar n…®na.
\q1 
\v 21 \x - \xo 2:21 \xt 1 Eghaghaniba 29:30; Esta 1:13; Jeremaia 27:5; Jems 1:5\x*N…® amozim ko aruem…®n dughiam gatifa,
\q2 egha n…® uab…® gumazibagh inabi, da atrivibar otifi,
\q3 egha n…® men ingangaribar me a gefi.
\q2 Egha fofozir aghuiba ko n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba gumazibagh an…®di.
\q1 
\v 22 \x - \xo 2:22 \xt Onger Akaba 139:11-12; Daniel 2:28-29; Hibru 4:13; Jems 1:17\x*Egha God n…® bizir aven modoghav itir me fozir puvat…®ziba men akakasi.
\q2 Ez…® zurara angazangarim n…®n iti,
\q3 ez…® n…® m…®tatem…®n itir biziba, n…® dagh fogha g…®fa.
\q1 
\v 23 Nan ovavibar God, n…® fofozim ko gavgavim na gan…®ngi
\q2 egha n…® nan d…®mdiam baraki,
\q3 egha bizir e n…®n azangs…®ghizir kam, en aka.
\q2 Egha n…® atrivim…®n irebam…®n m…®ngarim, en aka.
\q1 K…® bizir kam bagha n…® m…®nabagha, bar n…®n ziam fe.вАЭ
\s1 Daniel irebam…®n m…®ngarim…®n gun atrivim m…®gei
\p 
\v 24 Egha Daniel Ariok bagha ghu, gumazir kam atrivim Babilon…®n fofozir gumazibav sueght…® me aremeghasa anem…®sefe. Ez…® Daniel kamagh…®n a m…®gei, вАЬN…® fofozir gumazibav sueght…® me aremeghan mark…®. N…® na inigh atrivim bagh mang…®, eght…® k…® irebam…®n a geghan…®va irebam…®n m…®ngarim…®n gun a m…®k…®mam.вАЭ
\p 
\v 25 Ez…® zuam…®ra Ariok Daniel inigha atrivim bagha ghugha, kamagh…®n atrivim m…®gei, вАЬK…® Judan adarazir mav inigha izi, me fom…®ra kalabuziar gumazir mam…®n m…®n an kantrin a inigha kagh ize. Ez…® a irebam…®n m…®ngarim…®n gun n…® m…®k…®mam.вАЭ
\p 
\v 26 Ez…® Daniel, an ziar mam Beltesasar, atrivim kamagh…®n an azara, вАЬN…® nan irebam ko an m…®ngarim m…®k…®mamin fofozim iti?вАЭ
\p 
\v 27 Ez…® Daniel kamagh…®n atrivim m…®gei, вАЬAtrivim, fofozir gumazitam, ko kukunir gumazitam, ko imezibagh amir gumazitam, ko akuzibagh amir gumazitam, me bar modoghav tir bizir kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®gh…®va avegham.
\v 28 Ez…® God…®n Uan Nguibam…®n Itim, a iti, a bizir mogomebar m…®ngariba azenim gar…®si. Atrivim, God bizir g…®n otivamibar n…®n akaghasa irebar kam n…® gan…®ngi. Ez…® k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n irebar n…® uan dakozim…®n akua ganizim…®n, gun n…® m…®k…®mam.
\p 
\v 29 вАЬAtrivim, n…® akuima God irebam…®n bizir g…®n otivamiba n…®n aka. Ez…® God…®n kam, a bizir mogomeba azenim gar…®si. Egha bizir g…®n otivamiba n…®n aka.
\v 30 \x - \xo 2:30 \xt Jenesis 41:16; Daniel 2:47; Aposel 3:12\x*Egha God…®n kam bizir modoghav itim nan aka. K…®rara fofozir ekiam ikia egha fofozir gumazir igharazibagh afirazir pu. Puvat…®. God bizir kam nan aka, eght…® n…® uan irebam…®n m…®ngarim ko n…®ghn…®zibagh g…®fogham.
\p 
\v 31 вАЬAtrivim, n…® irebam…®n garima marvir guar dafam iti. Ez…® bizir kam a gavgavigha bar puv…®ra taghtasi. Ez…® n…® an ganigha bar atiatingi.
\v 32 Me gol…®n puv…®ra taghtazim…®n an dapanim…®n ingari. Egha an evarim ko agharimning, me silvan aning…®n ingari, egha an ivariam me bras…®n dar ingari.
\v 33 Egha an suemning me ain…®n aning…®n ingarigha, an dagarimning…®n v…®n, me uaghara ain ko nguazim veregha aning…®n ingari.
\v 34 Ez…® dughiar n…® marvir guar kam…®n garav…®ra itim…®n, dag…®am a uab…® m…®ghs…®am…®n kuiaghir…®, gumazitam a poghezir puvat…®. A uab…® izaghira marvir guar kam m…®sogha an dagarir me nguazim ko ain…®n ingarizimning m…®soke. Ez…® aning bar m…®saraghire.
\v 35 Ez…® ainba, ko nguazim, ko bras, ko silva, ko gol, da bar b…®aghiregha mati raiz…®n m…®seviba, n…® da isa da makuri. Ez…® am…®nim dagh ivavamadi, ez…® m…®nezir taba ua itir puvat…®. Ez…® dag…®ar marvir guar kam m…®soghezim, an aghua m…®ghs…®ar ekiam…®n otoghava nguazir kam bar anevara.
\p 
\v 36 вАЬKar irebar n…® ganizim. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® irebam…®n m…®ngarim…®n gun n…® m…®k…®mam.
\v 37 Atrivim, n…® faraghav…®ra ikia, egha atrivir maba bar dagh afira. Ez…® God…®n Uan Nguibam…®n Itim, a n…®n amamangat…®z…® n…® atrivim…®n iti. Ez…® a gavgavim n…® gan…®ga egha ziar ekiam n…® gan…®ngi.
\v 38 Egha n…® gamima, gumazamiziba bar, ko as…®ziba, ko kuaraziba bar, n…® me gatifa. Ez…® n…® dapanir me gol…®n ingarizim…®n m…®n iti.
\p 
\v 39 вАЬEght…® atrivir mam n…®n g…®n otivam, egh a n…®n m…®n gavgavighan kogham. Egh g…®n atrivir m…®kezim otogh…®va, nguazir oteviba bar dagh ativagham. Ez…® atrivir kam mati bras.
\v 40 Eght…® ua g…®n namba 4…®n atrivim otivam. An ain…®n m…®n gavgavigham. E fo, ain bizibav sozima da b…®gha m…®nemniaba iri. Ez…® kamagh…®ra atrivir kam kantrin fom…®ra ikezibar gavgaviba bar dagh afiragh ada g…®vagham.
\v 41 Ez…® n…® irebam…®n kamagh…®n gari, bizir kam…®n dagarimning ko dagarir puziba, me ain ko nguazim uaning veregha dar ingari. Ez…® bizir kam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n. Gumazamizir atrivir kam ativaziba, me uarira uari abigh, men tarazi gavgavigh ik…®v…®ra ikiam. Ain ko nguazim v…®rara dagarir pumuning…®n iti, a kamagh…®n n…®n aka, dar gavgavim ain…®n m…®n gavgavigh egh bar gavgavighan kogham.
\v 42 Ez…® dagarir puzir me ain ko nguazim…®n ingarizim, a kamak…®n, kantrin otevir mam ain…®n m…®n gavgavigham. Eght…® an otevir mam nguazim m…®n gavgavighan kogham.
\v 43 Ez…® me, nguazim ko ain aning veregha marvir guar kam…®n dagarim…®n ingari. Ez…® bizir kam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n. Atrivim gumazamizir b…®aghireziba, ua me akuvasa n…®ghn…®si. Eght…® me atrivir igharazibar guivibar ik…®, egh me deragh uari ko poroghan kogham.\f + \fr 2:43 \ft Aram…®n akam deragha akar otevir kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* Kamagh…®ra ain deragha nguazim ko pozir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 44 вАЬEz…® dughiar atrivir kaba ikiav…®ra itim…®n, God…®n Uan Nguibam…®n Itim, a Dughiar a Gumazamizibagh Ativaghamin Tam a damight…®, an otivam. Eght…® a ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam. Eght…® atrivir maba da God Gumazamizibagh Ativaghamin Dughiar Kam d…®kab…®raghan kogham. Eght…® God Gumazamizibagh Ativaghamin Dughiam, an atrivir igharazibagh as…®ghasigham. Eght…® an atrivir dughiar kam a ik…® mamagh…®ra ik…®v…®ra ikiam.
\v 45 N…® dag…®am…®n gari, a uab…® m…®ghs…®am…®n pura kuiaghir…®, gumazitam a poghezir puvat…®. Dag…®ar kam ira, marvir guar me ain ko bras ko nguazim ko silva ko gol…®n ingarizim a m…®soghez…®, a bar m…®saraghire. Dag…®ar kam, a God gumazamizibagh ativaghamin dughiam…®n ababanim.
\p вАЬGod…®n ziar ekiam itim, a bizir g…®n otivamiba n…®n aka. Guizbang…®ra, bizir n…® irebam…®n ganiziba, da k…® n…® m…®kemez…® mogh…®ram otivam.вАЭ
\s1 Atrivim ziar ekiam Daniel gan…®ngi
\p 
\v 46 Atrivim Nebukatnesar Daniel…®n akam baregha, egha Daniel…®n borogh…®ra tevimning ap…®righa ir…®gha uan guam isa nguazim gat…®gha ghaze, me Daniel…®n ofa damu borer mughuriar aghuim zuim tuva an ziam f…®.
\v 47 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n Daniel m…®gei, вАЬN…® irebar modozir kam…®n gun m…®kemegha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® kamagh…®n fo, n…®n God a god…®n igharazibagh afira. Ana atriviba bar dar ekiam, egha bizir mogomeba azenim gar…®si.вАЭ
\p 
\v 48 \x - \xo 2:48 \xt Daniel 2:6; 4:9; 5:11\x*Ez…® atrivim Babilon…®n provins…®n gavman…®n dapanim…®n ikiasa Daniel am…®sefe. Egh a gumazir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba atrivim gan…®dibar gumazir dapanim…®n iti. Ez…® atrivim uaghan Daniel bizir av…®rir aghuiba a gan…®ngi. Ez…® Daniel ziar ekiam iti.
\v 49 Egha Daniel Babilon…®n provins gatifa. Egha a ingangaribar ganasa n…®ghn…®ghava, Satrak ko Mesak ko Abetnego, me am…®s…®vasa atrivim…®n azangs…®si. Ez…® atrivim an azangs…®zir kam…®n amamangat…®z…®, me dar gari. Egha Daniel uab…® atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n iti.
\c 3
\s1 Nebukatnesar marvir guam…®n tevimning ap…®righ a ziam fasa gumazamizibav gei
\p 
\v 1 Atrivim Nebukatnesar m…®geima me gol inigha marvir guar mam…®n ingari. Ez…® marvir guar kam…®n ruarim a 27 mitan tuz…®, an baravim 3 mitan tu. Ez…® me marvir guar kam isa Babilon…®n provins…®n Duran nguazir zarim…®n anet…®.
\v 2 Ez…® me anet…®gha g…®vaz…®ma, atrivim uan gavman gumazir dapaniba bar me m…®g…®a ghaze, me iz…® uari akufagh. Eght…® gavman…®n faragha zuir gumaziba ko, gumazir dapaniba ko, gumazir ekiar faragh zuiba ko, nguibam…®n gavman…®n garir gumaziba ko, dag…®abar garir gumaziba ko, jasba ko, nguibabar gavman…®n gumaziba me iz…® uari akufagh. Me iz…®, marvir guar Atrivim Nebukatnesar asarazir kam bagh, dughiar faragha zuim…®n an ziam f…®s…® izam.
\v 3 Ez…® gavman…®n gumazir ekiar kaba iza bar marvir guam itir nagh…®n dughiar namba wan…®n an ziam fasa bar uari akufa.
\p 
\v 4 Egha gavman…®n gumazir akam akurir mam pamten kamagh…®n diagha m…®gei, вАЬIa nguibaba bar dar gumazamiziba, kantriba bar dar gumazamiziba, nguibabar akaba bar ia bar atrivim…®n akam baragh!
\v 5 Ia s…®ghaba ko mariviba ko gitaba ko buaba ko ighiar igharaziba baraght…® da arangam. Egh ia ighiar kam baragh, uan teviba p…®righ avigh marvir guar Atrivim Nebukatnesar asarazir kam…®n ziam f…®.
\v 6 Eght…® gumazitam tevimning ap…®righ aviragh, marvir guam…®n ziam fan koght…®, e zuam…®ra a inigh danganir ekiar avir bar pamten isim…®n aven anekunigham.вАЭ
\p 
\v 7 Kamagh…®n me ighiam baragha, nguibaba bar dar gumazamiziba ko kantriba bar dar gumazamiziba ko nguibabar akaba bar, magh…®ra teviba ap…®righa aviragha marvir guar Atrivim Nebukatnesar asarazir kam…®n ziam fe.
\s1 Me Judan gumazir 3plan gun m…®keme
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Babilon…®n gumazir maba iza Judan gumazamizibar ziabagh as…®ghas…®ghasa men gun atrivim m…®keme.
\v 9 Egha me kamagh…®n Atrivim Nebukatnesar…®n m…®gei, вАЬGumazir ekiam, n…® ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam!
\v 10 Atrivim, n…® gumazamiziba bar kamagh…®n me m…®g…®a ghaze, me s…®ghaba ko mariviba ko gitaba ko buaba ko ighiar igharaziba baragh…®va, gumazamiziba bar teviba ap…®righ avigh, gol…®n marvir guar n…® ingarigha asarazir kam…®n ziam fam.
\v 11 Eght…® gumazitam tevimning ap…®righ aviragh marvir guam…®n ziam fan koght…®, n…® zuam…®ra a inigh danganir ekiar avir bar pamten isim…®n aven anekunigham.
\v 12 Ez…® Judan gumazir pumuning ko m…®kezir kaba, Satrak, Mesak, ko Abetnego, kar n…® Babilon…®n provins gativagh an ganasa me am…®sefe, ez…® me n…®n akam batoke. Egha me n…®n asebar ziaba fer puvat…®, egha uaghan teviba ap…®righa aviragha gol…®n marvir guar n…® asarazir kam…®n ziam fer puvat…®.вАЭ
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® Atrivim Nebukatnesar akar kam baregha bar puv…®ram atara egha ghaze, ia 3plan gumazir kaba inigh na bagh iz…®.
\v 14 Me izegha g…®vaz…®ma a kamagh…®n men azai, вАЬSatrak ko Mesak ko Abetnego, me ghaze ia nan aseba ko god…®n marvir guar k…® asarazir kam ia uaghan teviba ap…®ra aviragha an ziam fer puvat…®. Guizbang…®ra, o?
\v 15 \x - \xo 3:15 \xt Ua Me Ini 5:2; 2 Atriviba 18:35\x*Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n, ia s…®ghaba ko mariviba ko gitaba ko buaba ko ighiar igharaziba baragh…®va, teviba p…®righ…®va avigh marvir guar kam…®n ziam f…®. Ia kamagh…®n damuan koght…®, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®ra gumazibav kemeght…® me ia is…® danganir ekiar avir bar pamten isim…®n aven ia kunigham. Eght…® god…®n manam ian akuragh nan gavgavim da ua ia inigham?вАЭ
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® Satrak, Mesak ko Abetnego atrivim ikara, вАЬAtrivim Nebukatnesar, bizir n…® e damuasa ifongezir kam, e akaba an puvat…®.
\v 17 E guiz…®n God…®n ziam fe. N…® m…®kemez…® mogh…®n e damigh, eght…® en God…®n gavgavim itim, an en akuraght…®, n…®n gavgavim ko danganir ekiar avir bar pamten isim, e a gitagham. God en akuragham.
\v 18 Eght…® an en akuraghan koght…®, n…® bizir kam g…®fogh, e n…®n asebar ziaba fan kogh…®va, egh uaghan teviba p…®righ…®va aviragh gol…®n marvir guar n…® asarazir kam…®n ziam fan kogham.вАЭ
\s1 Me Satrak, Mesak ko Abetnego isava avim m…®k…®ni
\p 
\v 19 Nebukatnesar akar kam baregha egha bar Satrak, Mesak ko Abetnego men an…®ngaghegha, an damazimning bar aghefe. Egha a uan ingangarir gumazibav kemeght…® me avim at…®ght…® a puv…®ra isiam. Avim faragha kamagh…®n isizir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 20 Egha a uan m…®dorozir gumazir gavgavibav g…®a ghaze, me Satrak, Mesak ko Abetnego, ikegh me is…®va danganir ekiar avir bar pamten isim…®n me kunigh.
\v 21 Kamagh…®n, me 3pla uaghara men korotiar ruariba ko siotba ko dapanir asuaba sara me ikeghava, me isa danganir ekiar avir bar pamten isim…®n, me akuni.
\v 22 Dughiar kam atrivim faragha m…®geima me avim gamima a bar pamtem…®n isia m…®zariaba zui. Kamagh…®n, m…®dorozir gumazir me inigha avir danganir ekiam…®n ghueziba, avir m…®zariaba bar men isiz…® me ariaghire.
\v 23 Ez…® Satrak, Mesak ko Abetnego, me avim…®n torim giraghue. Ez…® me ikezir beniba kamagh…®ra iti.
\p 
\v 24 Ez…® Atrivim Nebukatnesar men ganigha d…®gavir kuram gamigha zuam…®ra d…®kavigha tu. Egha kamagh…®n gumazir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba a gan…®dibar azara, вАЬE 3plan gumaziba ikegha me isa avim m…®k…®ni, o puvat…®?вАЭ Ez…® me a ikara, вАЬAre, atrivim, e manmagh…®ram ami.вАЭ
\p 
\v 25 Ez…® a ghaze, вАЬManmagh…®n amiz…® k…® 4plan gumazibar garima me avim…®n torim…®n arui? Egha benir e me ikeziba, ua men namnabar itir puvat…®. Egha avim uaghan men isir puvat…®. Ez…® namba 4…®n gumazim asebar borim…®n m…®n gari.вАЭ
\s1 Avim 3plan gumazibar isizir puvat…®
\p 
\v 26 Ez…® Nebukatnesar danganir ekiar avir bar pamten isim…®n tiar akam…®n borogh…®ra ghugha kamagh…®n dei, вАЬSatrak! Mesak! Abetnego! Ia God…®n Bar P…®n Itim…®n ingangarir gumaziba! Ia azenan iz…®!вАЭ Ez…® me avim ategha azenan ize.
\v 27 Ez…® gavman…®n faragha zuir gumaziba ko, gumazir dapaniba ko, gumazir aruar faragh zuiba ko, gumazir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba atrivim gan…®diba, me iza Judan gumazir 3plan kabar ganasa uari akufa. Me gara fo, me isizir puvat…®. Egha avim men dapanir ar…®ziba ko korotiabar isizir puvat…®, egha me m…®karzitam isigha mughazir puvat…®, egha avir mughuriar tam zuir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 28 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n m…®gei, вАЬE bar Satrak, Mesak, ko Abetnego, men God…®n ziam fam. God uan ensel amadaz…® a 3plan gumazir an ziam fa egha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an itibar akura. Me nan akam batuegha ovengan atiatingizir puvat…®. Egha god…®n igharazitam tevimning ap…®righa an ziam feir puvat…®. Me uan God…®n ziamra fe.
\v 29 Ez…® k…® fo, Satrak, Mesak ko Abetnego, men God men akuraz…® mogh…®n, god…®n igharaz tam uan gumazamizibar akuraghan kogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam damuasa, ia gumazamiziba bar God…®n kam a d…®pova, akar kuratam…®n a m…®k…®man kogham. Egh nguibaba bar dar gumazamiziba ko kantriba bar dar gumazamiziba ko nguibabar akaba bar, me arazir kam damut…®, k…® m…®dorozir gumazibav kemeght…® me men sueba ko aghariba asight…®, me aremegham. Egh me men d…®peniba akarar…®gh bar dagh as…®ghas…®gham.вАЭ
\p 
\v 30 Ez…® atrivim m…®kemegha g…®vagha, egha Satrak, Mesak ko Abetnego ingangarir igiam Babilon…®n provins…®n me gan…®ngi, ingangarir kam ingangarir me faragha amizim gafira.
\c 4
\s1 Nebukatnesar…®n namba 2…®n irebam, a temer ekiam…®n gani
\p 
\v 1 Atrivim Nebukatnesar nguazim…®n nguibaba bar dar gumazamiziba ko kantriba bar dar gumazamiziba ko nguibabar akaba bar, me bagha akam amada. An akam kamak…®n:
\b
\pi1 Ia bar deraghv…®ra ik…®!
\b
\pi1 
\v 2 Dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® arazaraziba ko mirakel…®n bar ekiaba, God…®n Bar P…®n Itim na bagha dagh amizibar gun ia m…®k…®masa.
\b
\q1 
\v 3 God arazarazir bar ekiabar en aka!
\q2 Egha bar gavgavigha mirakel bagh ami!
\q1 God ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam;
\q2 an atrivim…®n dughiaba zurara ik…®v…®ra ikiam.
\b
\pi1 
\v 4 K…® Nebukatnesar, n…®m…®ra uan d…®penim…®n aperaghav ikia uan ingangaribar garima, da bar deragha oto. Egha k…® bizir av…®rim ikia, egha bar akuegha iti.
\v 5 Ez…® d…®magarir mam…®n k…® irebam…®n ganigha bar puv…®ram atiatingi. K…® irebam…®n aven ganizir biziba na gamiz…® k…® d…®gavir kuram gami.
\v 6 Egha k…® Babilon…®n fofozir gumaziba bagha akam amada, eght…® me izi irebam…®n m…®ngarim…®n gun na m…®k…®mam.
\v 7 Ez…® irebar m…®ngaribagh fogha dar gun m…®geir gumaziba ko, kukunir gumaziba ko, imezibagh amir gumaziba ko, akavsiabagh amir gumaziba, me bar ize. K…® irebam…®n gun me m…®geima, me irebam…®n m…®ngarim…®n gun na m…®k…®man ibura.
\v 8 Ez…® g…®n Daniel izi. (An ziar mam Beltesasar, ziar kam nan asem…®n ziam. Guizbang…®ra, aser bar gavgavibar duaba n…®ghn…®zim Daniel gan…®ngi.) Ez…® k…® uan irebam…®n gun a m…®gei. K…® kamagh…®n a m…®gei:
\pi1 
\v 9 вАЬBeltesasar, fofozir gumazibar gumazir dapanim, k…® fo, aser bar gavgavibar duaba, n…®ghn…®zim n…® gan…®ngiz…®, ez…® bizitam n…®n p…®n kogh, n…®n modoghan kogham. Ez…® n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n nan irebam baragh, egh an m…®ngarim…®n gun na m…®k…®m.
\pi1 
\v 10 вАЬK…® uan dakozim gir…®ghav ikia irebam…®n garima, temer bar dafam nguazim bar mogh…®ra an tong…®ra tughav iti.
\v 11 Egha an aghua bar ek…®va ghuanaga overiam…®n suira, nguazim…®n itir gumazamiziba bar an gari.
\v 12 Ez…® temer kam dafarir bar aghuiba iti, egha ov…®zir av…®riba iti, nguazim…®n itir gumazamiziba bar dar amegh iz…®vagham. Ez…® kuaraziba an aguabar m…®konibagh amima, nguazim…®n as…®zir atiaba iza an apengan avughsi, egha da bar an ov…®ziba api.
\pi1 
\v 13 вАЬK…® uan dakozim gir…®ghav ikia irebam…®n garav…®ra itima ensel…®n mam God…®n Nguibam…®n ikegha izaghiri, an ensel…®n maba ko me bizibar garir enselba.
\v 14 Egha pamtem…®n d…®a ghaze: N…® temem okeght…® a ir…®gh. Egh an aguaba aghoregh, an dafariba aghor da makunigh, an ov…®ziba tintinibar da kunigh. Egh as…®zir an apebam…®n itiba batokegh, egh kuarazir an aguabar itiba batokegh.
\v 15 Egh temer dakam biba saram aneteght…® a nguazim…®n grazibar tong…®n ik…®, eght…® ain…®n kuakar ekiatam ko bras inigh an povim gighuigh. Egh gumazir kam ateght…® amariba d…®magaribar a giram. Eght…® an as…®zibar m…®n dadabar am…® ikiam.
\v 16 Egh gumazir kam, a 7plan azenibar gumazamiziba n…®ghn…®zi mogh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan kogham, ana as…®zibar m…®n n…®ghn…®gh ikiam.
\v 17 Ez…® bizibar garir enselba bizir kaba otivasa me m…®keme, eght…® angam…®ra itir gumazamiziba bar kamagh…®n fogham, God…®n Bar P…®n Itim bar gumazamizibagh ativagha men gari. Egha a uab…® uan ifongiam…®n g…®n ghua, gumazir ziar ekiaba itiba ko gumazir k…®niba, atrivim…®n ikiasa me am…®sevima me otifi.вАЭ
\b
\p 
\v 18 Egha k…® ua kamagh…®n Daniel m…®gei, k…® uan irebam n…® m…®kemegha g…®fa. Nan fofozir gumaziba irebam…®n m…®ngarim…®n gun na m…®k…®man ibura. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Beltesasar, n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n an m…®ngarim…®n gun na m…®k…®mam. K…® fo, aser bar gavgavibar duaba n…®ghn…®zim n…® gan…®ngi, kamagh…®n n…®rara na m…®k…®mam.
\s1 Daniel irebam…®n m…®ngarim…®n gun m…®gei
\p 
\v 19 Ez…® Daniel irebam…®n m…®ngarim g…®fogha g…®fa, kamagh…®n amiz…®ma a bar osemegha d…®gavir kuram gamigha, atrivim…®n m…®k…®man atiati.\f + \fr 4:19 \ft Akar kam, 4:19…®n ikegha ghua 4:33…®n tu, kar akar otevir mam Atrivim Nebukatnesar gumazamiziba bagha anemada. (N…® Daniel 4:1…®n ganigh.) Egha kagh atrivim bizir a bativizibagh eghanizir puvat…®.\f* Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n a m…®gei, вАЬBeltesasar, irebar kam ko an m…®ngarim n…® damut…® n…® os…®m…®va atiatingan mark…®.вАЭ
\p Ez…® Beltesasar a ikara, вАЬAtrivim, k…® irebar kam m…®kemezir biziba n…® bativan k…® ifongezir puvat…®. Da n…®n apanibara otivasa k…® ifonge!
\v 20 N…® temer ekiar mam…®n gani, a bar ruaragha ghuanaga overiam…®n suira, ez…® nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba bar an gari.
\v 21 A dafarir bar aghuiba ko ov…®zir av…®riba iti, nguazim…®n itir gumazamiziba bar dar amegh iz…®vagham. Ez…® as…®zir atiaba an apengan avughsi, ez…® kuaraziba an aguabar m…®konibar ingari.
\p 
\v 22 вАЬAtrivim, n…®rara temer kam, ruaragha bar gavgafi. Ez…® n…®n gavgavim bar ekevegha p…®n ti, ez…® n…®n gavgavim nguazim…®n itir gumazamiziba bar dar gari.
\p 
\v 23 вАЬEz…® n…® garima, ensel…®n mam God…®n Nguibam…®n ikegha izaghira ghaze, вАШN…® temer kam okegh a gas…®ghas…®kigh, egh an dakam ateght…® a nguazim…®n ik…®. Egh ain…®n kokam ko bras inigh an povim gighuigh. Eght…® ghuariar d…®paba d…®mangan gumazir kam giram, egh aneteght…® a 7plan azenibar as…®zir atiaba ko ikiam.вАЩ
\p 
\v 24 вАЬAtrivim, irebar kam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n, kar God…®n Bar P…®n Itim m…®kemezir bizim, n…® bativam.
\v 25 N…® gumazamizibar nguibam ategh, mang…®va as…®zir atiaba ko ikiam. N…® bulmakaubar m…®n dadabar am…®, egh puram azenan dakuam. Eght…® d…®magarim…®n ghuariar d…®paba 7plan azenibar n…® giram. N…® kamagh…®ra ik…®, mang…® kamagh…®n fogham, God…®n Bar P…®n Itim bar gumazamizibagh atifa. Ez…® a uab…® uan ifongiam…®n, gumaziba m…®sevima me atrivibar otifi.
\v 26 N…® ensel barazi, a temer dakam ateght…® a nguazim…®n aven ikiasa m…®keme. Bizir kam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n, n…® bar kamagh…®n fogh m…®k…®m, God Uab…®ra Nguazim…®n Biziba Bar Dagh Atifa. N…® fogha g…®fa, egha g…®n n…® uam atrivim…®n otivam.
\v 27 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, atrivim, n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® n…® m…®k…®mamin akam…®n g…®n mangam:\f + \fr 4:27 \ft Gumazir maba ghaze, vez…®n kam, a dughiar Nebukatnesar uam atrivim…®n otivamim a m…®geir puvat…®. Me ghaze, Daniel kamagh…®n m…®keme, atrivim arazir aghuibar amut…®, bizir kurar kaba a bativan kogham.\f* N…® arazir kurabar amuan kogh…®va, arazir aghuibar amu, egh gumazamizir onganarazibar apangkuf. N…® kamagh…®n damuva, egh n…® ti deraghv…®ra ik…®t…®, bizir n…® amiba bar derav…®ram otivam.вАЭ
\p 
\v 28 Ez…® Daniel m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra, bizir kaba bar Atrivim Nebukatnesar batifi.
\v 29 Ez…® 12plan iak…®niba g…®vaz…®, atrivim dughiar mam…®n uan d…®penir Babilon…®n itim…®n azuarim garui.
\v 30 Egha kamagh…®n m…®gei, вАЬIa gan, Babilon a nguibar bar ekiam egha bar dera. Nan gavgavim…®n k…® uab…® an ingari, k…® nguibar kam gamiz…® an otogha, uan gavgavim ko ziar ekiam is…® gumazamizibar akakaghasa.вАЭ
\p 
\v 31 A m…®g…®av…®ra ikiava egha orazima, tiarir mam God…®n Nguibam…®n ikegha izi. Tiarir kam kamagh…®n m…®gei, вАЬAtrivim Nebukatnesar, n…® nan akam barakigh. Kantrin n…® ativazir kam, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n n…® dam a inigham.
\v 32 Eght…® k…® n…® batueght…® n…® ua gumazamiziba ko ikian kogham. N…® mang…® as…®zir atiaba ko ikiam. Egh n…® 7plan azenibar, bulmakaubar m…®n dadabar amam. N…® kamagh…®ra ik…® mang…® dughiar n…® fogh suam, God…®n Bar P…®n Itim bar gumazamizibagh atifa. A uab…® uan ifongiam…®n, gumazibagh amima me atrivibar otifi.вАЭ
\p 
\v 33 Ez…® bizir ensel m…®kemeziba, da zuam…®ra Nebukatnesar batifi. Me gumazamizibar tong…®n a batoghez…®, a bulmakaubar m…®n dadaba api. Egha d…®magarim…®n ghuariar d…®paba an namnam giri. Egha an dapanir ar…®zim bar ruaragha taragiar ar…®zibar m…®n gari. Egha an dafarir puziba bar ruaragha mati kuarazir puzibar m…®n gari.
\s1 Nebukatnesar God…®n ziam fe
\pi1 
\v 34 G…®n 7plan azeniba g…®vaz…®, k…® Nebukatnesar, k…® kogha God…®n nguibam…®n gara, egha nan n…®ghn…®ziba ua dera. Egha k…® God…®n Bar P…®n Itim bagha bar akonge. A God…®n ikia mamagh…®ra itim, kamagh…®n, k…® an ziam fam. Egha k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei:
\b
\q1 God atrivim…®n ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam.
\q2 Eght…® an atrivir kam dughiabar ik…®v…®ra ikiam.
\q1 
\v 35 A gari, nguazim…®n itir gumazamiziba mati
\q2 pura biziba.
\q1 An Nguibam…®n itir enselba ko nguazim…®n itir gumazamiziba an apengan iti,
\q2 a bar me gatifa.
\q1 Egh a bizitam damus…® an a damuam,
\q2 eght…® gumazitam an anogoreghan kogham.
\q1 Guizbang…®ra, gumazitam kamagh…®n an azangs…®ghan kogham,
\q2 N…® bizir tizim gami. Bar puvat…®.
\b
\p 
\v 36 Ez…® k…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam gamir dughiam…®n, nan n…®ghn…®zim ua dera, ez…® k…® ua uan ziar ekiam ini. Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® kantrin faragha ativazim, k…® uam a gativagh an ganamin gavgavim ini. Ez…® gumazir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba na gan…®diba, ko nan gumazir ekiaba, me ua iza na ko iti. Ez…® k…® uam atrivim…®n ikia, egha ziar bar ekiam iti, a ziar ekiar k…® faragha inizim gafira.
\p 
\v 37 Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® Nebukatnesar, k…® Atrivir Uan Nguibam…®n Itim bagha bar akonge, egha an ziam fa ziar ekiam a gan…®di. K…® fo, bizir ana amiba bar vorogh…®ra ikia bar dera. Egha a gumazir uan ziaba feba da d…®kab…®ri.
\c 5
\s1 Atrivim Belsasar…®n isar ekiam
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Belsasar atrivir igiam…®n otogha, d…®magarir mam…®n a isar ekiar mam gamua, egha uan gumazir ekiar tausen plan diaz…® me isar kam…®n izegha, a ko wain…®n d…®pam api.
\v 2 Egha me wain…®n d…®pam apav…®ra itima, Belsasar, gol kapba ko silvan kapba inigh izasa uan ingangarir gumazibav m…®gei. Kav…®n kaba, an afeziam Nebukatnesar Jerusalem…®n nguibam…®n itir God…®n D…®penim…®n ghugha da inigha Babilon…®n nguibam…®n ize. Atrivim ghaze, a uan gumazir ekiaba ko uan amuiba ko an amuir doziba ko, me bar kav…®n kabar wain…®n d…®pabar amam.
\v 3 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ingangarir gumaziba gol…®n kapba inigha ize. Ez…® gumazamiziba bar kav…®n kabar wain…®n d…®paba api.
\v 4 Egha me wain…®n d…®paba apa ikiava, aser me gol, ko silva, ko bras, ko ain, ko temem, ko dag…®am…®n, ingarizir marvir guabar ziaba fe.
\p 
\v 5 Me kamagh…®n amima, gumazim…®n dafarim zuam…®ra b…®rim…®n otogha b…®rim gis…®n osiri. Danganir kam…®n lam isia an angazangarim bar ekefe, ez…® atrivim bar deraghav…®ra dafarir kam…®n garima, an osiri.
\v 6 Egha a bar atiatigha, an atiatir guam asaragha, an gavgavim g…®vaz…®, an soroghafariba a gin…®si.
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® a kukunir gumaziba, ko imezibagh amir gumaziba, ko akavsiar ifavaribagh amir gumaziba, tav a bagh me inigh izasa a pamten dei. Me izegha g…®vaz…®ma, atrivim kamagh…®n me m…®gei, вАЬGumazitam akar kam d…®ponegh an m…®ngarim…®n gun na m…®kemeght…®, k…® atrivim…®n korotiar aghevim a danight…® aneghuam. Egh k…® gol…®n sen an f…®rim…®n daght…®, a ziar ekiam iniam. Eght…® k…® a damight…® a namba 3…®n gavman…®n gumazim…®n ikiam.вАЭ
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® fofozir gumaziba aven izegha g…®vaz…®, atrivim akar kam bar me m…®kemez, men tav akar kam d…®ponan ibura. Egha men tav akar kam…®n m…®ngarim…®n gun atrivim m…®kemezir puvat…®.
\v 9 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Atrivim Belsasar bar atiatingi. Egha an atiatir guam asaragha an gavgavim g…®vaz…®ma, an soroghafariba a gin…®si. Ez…® an gumazir ekiaba n…®ghn…®ghava avenge, kamagh…®n amiz…®, me bizitam damuan ibura.
\p 
\v 10 Dughiar kam atrivim…®n amebam n…®g…®nir kam baraki, n…®g…®nir atrivim uan gumazir ekiaba ko me amizim. Egha a isar ekiam itir danganim…®n aven ghugha ghaze, вАЬAtrivim, n…® deraghv…®ra ik…® mamagh…®ra ik…®. N…® bizir kam ateght…® an os…®mt…®zim n…® dan…®ngan mark…®.
\v 11 N…® oragh, gumazir mam n…®n kantrin iti, ez…® aser bar gavgavibar duaba n…®ghn…®zim a gan…®ngi. Ez…® dughiar n…®n afeziam atrivim…®n itim…®n, n…®n afeziam gumazir kam…®n garima, a fofozir ekiaba ko n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba iti. Egha an fofozim bar ekevegha aser gavgavibar fofozim…®n m…®n ghu. Ez…® n…®n afeziam Atrivim Nebukatnesar, gumazir kam isa, irebabar m…®ngaribar gun m…®geir gumaziba ko, kukunir gumaziba, ko imezibagh amir gumaziba, ko akavsiar ifavaribagh amir gumaziba, bar men gumazir dapanim…®n ikiasa anem…®sefe. N…®n afeziam kamagh…®n ami.
\v 12 A fo, gumazir kam bar fofozir aghuiba ko n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba iti, egha irebabar m…®ngariba ko akar is…®n zuiba, ko bizir mogomebar m…®ngaribar gun m…®gei. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® Daniel bagh akam amadagh. Atrivim Nebukatnesar ziam Beltesasar a gat…®. N…® a m…®kemeght…® a iz…® akar b…®rim…®n itim…®n m…®ngarim…®n gun n…® m…®k…®mam.вАЭ
\s1 Daniel akar d…®penir b…®rim…®n itim…®n m…®ngarim…®n gun m…®gei
\p 
\v 13 Egha me Daniel inigha aven ghuz…®ma, an atrivim…®n borogh…®n tughav iti. Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n a m…®gei, вАЬN…® Daniel, n…® ti Judan gumazir mam? N…® ti Judan adarazir mav, fom…®ra nan afeziam, Atrivim Nebukatnesar, n…® inigha ize?
\v 14 K…® kamagh…®n oraki, aser bar gavgavibar duaba n…®ghn…®zim n…® gan…®ngi, ez…® n…® fofozir ekiaba ko n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba iti.
\v 15 K…® fofozir gumaziba ko kukunir gumazibar dia, eght…® me iz…® akar b…®rim…®n itim d…®pon…®va, an m…®ngarim gun na m…®k…®masa. Ez…® puvat…®, me m…®k…®man ibura.
\v 16 Ez…® k…® kamagh…®n oraki, n…® bizir mogomeba ko akar is…®n zuibar gun m…®gei. Egh n…® osizirir kam d…®pon…®va an m…®ngarim gun na m…®kemeght…®, k…® atrivim…®n korotiar aghevim n…® da arugh, egh gol sen n…®n f…®rim…®n dat…®ght…® n…® ziar ekiam iniam. Eght…® n…® nan gavman…®n gumazir namba 3…®n otogham.вАЭ
\p 
\v 17 Ez…® Daniel an akam ikaragha ghaze, вАЬMark…®, k…® n…® da bizir aghuitam inighan kogham. N…® ifuegh…®va, gumazir igharazir tam dan…®ngigh. Ez…® Atrivim, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n osizirir kam d…®pon…®va an m…®ngarim…®n gun n…® m…®k…®mam.
\p 
\v 18 вАЬN…® oragh. God…®n Bar P…®n Itim, a n…®n afeziam Nebukatnesar gamiz…®, a bar atrivir ekiam…®n otogha bar gavgafi, egha ziar ekiam ikia bar p…®n ti.
\v 19 A gavgavir bar ekiam iti, kamagh…®n amiz…®, nguibaba bar dar gumazamiziba ko, kantriba bar dar gumazamiziba ko, nguibabar akaba bar, me an atiatigha egha n…®si. Eght…® a gumazitam m…®sueght…® an aremeghs…® an aremegham. Eght…® a gumazitam ateght…® a ik…®s…®, a ikiam. Egha a kamagh…®n ami, a gumazitam…®n ziam f…®s…®, a fam. Eght…® a gumazitam d…®kab…®ragh a gas…®ghas…®ghs…®, ana damuam.
\v 20 Egha a uan ziam fava, akaba batogha, arazir igharazibagh amima, God…®n Ikiav…®ra Itim, atrivim…®n ikian a batoke, ez…® an ziar ekiam iraghuz…®, a uan danganim ataki.
\v 21 Ez…® God…®n Ikiav…®ra Itim gumazamizibar nguibam…®n a batoke, ez…® an n…®ghn…®zim, gumaziba n…®ghn…®zi mogh…®n n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®, an as…®zibar m…®n n…®ghn…®si. Egha a ghua donkiba ko ikia, bulmakaubar m…®n dadaba apava, puram azenan akui. Ez…® d…®magarim…®n ghuariar d…®paba a giri. Ez…® a kamagh…®n amua ghua g…®n a kamagh…®n fo, God…®n Bar P…®n Itim gumazamiziba bar me gativagha men gari. Egha a uab…® uan ifongiam…®n gumaziba m…®sevima me atrivibar otifi.
\p 
\v 22 \x - \xo 5:22 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 33:23; 36:12\x*вАЬN…® Nebukatnesar…®n otarim, n…® bizir kabagh fogha g…®fa. Egha n…® uab…® d…®kab…®razir puvat…®.
\v 23 N…® uab…® uan ziam fasa n…®ghn…®gha, Ekiar Uan Nguibam…®n Itim, n…® nan ziam d…®kab…®ra. Egha uan ingangarir gumazibav kemez…® me kav…®n n…®n afeziam God…®n D…®penim…®n iniziba inigha ize. Egha n…® uan gumazir ekiaba ko uan amuiba ko n…®n amuir doziba ko, ia bar kav…®n kabar wain…®n d…®paba api. Egha ia marvir guar me gol ko, silva ko, bras ko, ain ko, temeba ko, dag…®am…®n ingarizibar ziaba fe. Ez…® marvir guar kaba me garir puvat…®gha m…®g…®r…®g…®aba barazir puvat…®gha bizitam g…®fozir puvat…®. God uab…®ra n…®n ik…®r…®m…®rim ko n…® amir biziba bar dar gara dagh atifa. Ez…® n…® an ziam fer puvat…®.
\v 24 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, God dafarir kam amadaz…® an akar kaba osiri.
\v 25 Akar kam kamak…®n:
\b
\pc вАШD…®pon, d…®pon, tuis…®gh, ab…®kigh.вАЩ
\b
\q1 
\v 26 вАЬAkar kam…®n m…®ngarim, вАШD…®pon,вАЩ a kamak…®n,
\q2 God n…® atrivim…®n ikiamin dughiaba d…®pons…®.
\q3 Dat…®r…®gh…®n n…®n dughiar abuananam.
\q1 
\v 27 Ez…® akar kam…®n m…®ngarim, вАШTuis…®gh,вАЩ a kamak…®n,
\q2 God n…®n araziba tuisigha g…®fa, ez…® an ababanim kamagh…®n n…®n aka,
\q3 n…® arazir aghuibagh amir puvat…®.
\q1 
\v 28 Ez…® akar kam…®n m…®ngarim, вАШAb…®kigh,вАЩ a kamak…®n,
\q2 God n…®n kantri ab…®ghiz…®, an vuer mam Midian kantrin ghu,
\q3 ez…® an vuer mam Persian kantrin ghu.вАЭ\f + \fr 5:28 \ft Aram…®n akam…®n, akar kam вАЬAb…®kigh,вАЭ a Persian kantrin ziam…®n m…®rara ghu.\f*
\b
\p 
\v 29 Ez…® Atrivim Belsasar zuam…®ra uan ingangarir gumazibav geima, me korotiar aghevim Daniel garugha egha gol…®n sen an f…®rim…®n da. Egha Daniel gamiz…® a Belsasar…®n gavman…®n namba 3…®n gumazir dapanir ekiam…®n oto.
\p 
\v 30 Ez…® d…®magarir kamra, Midian kantrin gumaziba iza Babilon…®n Atrivim Belsasar…®n m…®soghez…® ana areme.
\v 31 Ez…® Darius, a Midian gumazim, a 62plan azeniba ikiava, dat…®r…®gh…®n Babilon…®n atrivim…®n oto, egha kantrin kam gativagha an gari.
\c 6
\s1 Me Daniel akuniz…® a laionba itir mozim giraghu
\p 
\v 1 Dughiar kam Darius atrivim…®n otogha g…®vagha, egha 120plan gavman…®n faragha zuir gumaziba am…®seveght…® me kantrin aven tir nguibabagh ativagh dar ganam.
\v 2 Ez…® atrivim, Daniel ko gumazir igharazir pumuning a me am…®sevez…®, me gavman…®n faragha zuir gumazir kabagh ativagh, atrivim…®n ingangaribar ganam. Eght…® atrivim…®n ingangaribar tong…®n bizitam ovengan kogham.
\v 3 Ez…® atrivim, Daniel…®n ingangarim…®n garima a bar dera, egha gavman…®n faragha zuir gumaziba ko a ko ingarir gumazimning a men ingangaribagh afira. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, atrivim…®n n…®ghn…®zim a Daniel am…®seveght…® a kantrin gumazir dapanim…®n ikiam.
\v 4 Ez…® gavman…®n faragha zuir gumazir kaba ko, Daniel ko ingangarir vam…®ram amimning, me n…®ghn…®zir kam gifongezir puvat…®. Egha me Daniel…®n ingangarim…®n aven gari, a bizitam paz…®va a damight…®, me a kot dar…®gham. Me garima, Daniel a gumazir bar aghuim, egha an ingangarim bar dera. A ifarir puvat…®gha arazir kuratam gamizir puvat…®, kamagh…®n amiz…®, me an arazir kuratam…®n apizir puvat…®.
\v 5 Egha me uarira uariv gei, вАЬE Daniel…®n ingangarim…®n aven arazir kuratam batoghan kogh egh, a kot dar…®gh…®va avegham. Egh arazir a uan God…®n g…®n ghua amibar gan…®va, tuavitam batogh…®va a kot dar…®gham.вАЭ
\p 
\v 6 Egha me atrivim…®n ganasa ghugha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, вАЬAtrivim Darius, n…® deraghv…®ra ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam!
\v 7 Ez…® e bar, n…®n gumazir ekiar n…®n kantri gativamiba, e gavman…®n gumazir dapaniba, ko gavman…®n faragha zuir gumaziba, ko distrigh…®n faragha zuir gumaziba, e bar, n…® akar bar gavgavitam damuasa, e akam ak…®righa g…®fa. En ifongiam kamak…®n, n…® gumazamiziba bar me m…®k…®m, eght…® 30plan dughiaba me bizitam bagh ase tam o gumazitam ko m…®k…®man mark…®. Me n…®rara n…® ko m…®k…®m. Eght…® gumazitam akar gavgavir kam batueght…®, n…® anekunight…® a laionba itir mozim…®n mag…®r…®.
\v 8 Ez…® atrivim, n…® gumazibav kemeght…® me akar gavgavir kam ak…®nafarim…®n an osiright…®, n…® uan ziam osiright…® an akar gavgavir kam a damut…® a gavgavigham. Eght…® gumazamiziba bar an g…®n mangam. Akar kam e Midia ko Persia, a en akar gavgavim, an e bagh ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam. Gumazitam anebighan kogham.вАЭ
\v 9 Ez…® Atrivim Darius gumazibav geima me akar kam osiriz…®, a uan ziam ak…®nafarir kam…®n an osiri.
\p 
\v 10 Egha Daniel atrivim…®n akam baregha fo, Atrivim uan ziam osiri. Egha zurarama ami mogh…®n, a d…®kavigha uan d…®penim…®n ghu. Egha a bar ghuriam…®n p…®n itir danganim…®n ghugha, winduan Jerusalem…®n amadaghan itim…®n bar an borogh…®ra tevimning ap…®righa, God ko m…®g…®a egha an ziam fe. A dughiar vam…®ra, 3plan dughiabar God ko m…®gei.
\v 11 Ez…® Daniel…®n apaniba bar mogh…®ra uari inigha, an d…®penim…®n ghua an garima, a uan God ko m…®gei.
\v 12 Egha me uamategha atrivim bagha ghugha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, вАЬAtrivim, guizbang…®ra n…® ghaze, gumazamiziba 30plan dughiabar n…®rara m…®k…®mam. Egh me asetam o gumazitam ko m…®k…®man kogham. Gumazitam akar gavgavir kam batueght…®, n…® anekunight…® a laionba itir mozim…®n ag…®ram.вАЭ
\p Ez…® atrivim ghaze, вАЬAre. Akar gavgavir kam tugha bar gavgafi, kar Midia ko Persian akar gavgavim, a ik…®v…®ra ikiam.вАЭ
\p 
\v 13 Egha me atrivim m…®gei, вАЬDaniel, gumazir kam Judan adarazir mav, me fom…®ra kalabuziar gumazir mam…®n m…®n an kantrin a inigha kagh ize, a n…®n akaba batogha, n…® at…®zir akar gavgavim…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®. A zurara 3plan dughiar vam…®ran, dughiar 3plan dughiabar dughiar vam…®ran uan God ko m…®gei.вАЭ
\v 14 Ez…® atrivim akar kam baregha an navim bar oseme, egha Daniel…®n akurvaghasa tuaviba buria ghuav…®ra itima am…®nim p…®ri.
\p 
\v 15 Ez…® Daniel…®n apaniba uamategha atrivim bagha izegha kamagh…®n pamten a m…®gei, вАЬAtrivim, n…® e Midia ko Persian arazim g…®fo. A kamak…®n, atrivim akar gavgavitam damight…®, akar gavgavir kam ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam.вАЭ
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® atrivim gumazibav geima, me Daniel inigha laionbar mozim…®n anekuniz…® a iraghu. Ez…® a kamagh…®n Daniel m…®gei, вАЬN…®n God…®n n…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ikia egha zurara teviba ap…®ra an ziam fer kam, a n…®n akuragh.вАЭ
\p 
\v 17 Ez…® me Daniel akunigha g…®vagha, dag…®ar ekiar mam inigha mozir akam ap…®ri. Egha atrivim uan gumazir dapaniba ko, me uan ring…®n dafaribagh aghuizir ababaniba isa dag…®ar kam gat…®. Egha bizitam Daniel damuan gumazamizibar anogoroke.
\v 18 Egha g…®n atrivim uamategha uan d…®penim…®n ghu. Egha d…®magarir kam…®n daghetam amezir puvat…®gha, gumazamizibar diaz…® me iza a koma aperazir puvat…®. Egha a uaghan akuava avenge. Bar puvat…®.
\p 
\v 19 Ez…® am…®nim tiraz…®ma bar m…®zaraghara atrivim d…®kavigha zuam…®ra ghua mozim…®n ghu.
\v 20 Ana otogha g…®vagha, bar osemegha kamagh…®n dei, вАЬDaniel, n…® God…®n Ikia Mamagh…®ra Itim…®n ingangarir gumazim! N…®n God…®n n…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ikia zurara teviba ap…®ra an ziam fer kam, a n…®n akuragha laionbar akabar kuaz…®, da n…® amez…® o puvat…®?вАЭ
\p 
\v 21 Ez…® Daniel mozim…®n aven ikia kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, вАЬAtrivim, n…® deraghv…®ra ik…® mamagh…®ra ik…®!
\v 22 God uan ensel amadaz…® a iza laionbar akabar kuaz…® da na gas…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®. A fo k…® deraghav…®ra ikia, egha arazir kuratam n…® gamizir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n, a nan akura.вАЭ
\p 
\v 23 Ez…® atrivim bar akuegha laionbar mozim…®n Daniel gekuigh azenim dar…®ghasa gumazibav gei. Me mozim…®n a gekuigha azenim gat…®gha g…®vagha, an garima, Daniel guizbang…®ra n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n iti, kamagh…®n amiz…®, laionba duatam a gat…®zir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 24 Ez…® atrivim m…®geima me gumazir Daniel isa kot gat…®zir kaba ko, men amuiba ko boriba inigha laionbar mozim m…®k…®ni. Ez…® me t…®ghar nguazim giram, laionba p…®rara men suigha men m…®karziba aghoraghsua men aghariba orovoregha me tuvareme.
\p 
\v 25 Ez…® Atrivim Darius, nguazir kam…®n itir nguibaba bar dar gumazamiziba ko kantriba bar dar gumazamiziba ko nguibabar akaba bar me bagha ak…®nafarim osira ghaze:
\b
\q1 вАЬIa bar navir am…®rizim…®n ik…®!
\q1 
\v 26 K…® kamagh…®n ia m…®gei, ia nan kantrin gumazamizir k…® ativaziba,
\q2 ia ziar ekiam Daniel…®n God dan…®ng,
\q3 egh God…®n kam…®n atiating an apengan ik…®.
\b
\q1 вАЬKar God…®n Ikia Mamagh…®ra Itim,
\q2 egh an atrivim…®n ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam.
\q3 An Dughiar an Atrivim…®n Ikiamim ko an gavgavim g…®vaghan kogham.
\q1 
\v 27 A gumazamizibar akurvagha ua me isi;
\q2 an arazaraziba ko mirakelba overiam ko nguazim…®n dagh ami.
\q1 Bar guizbang…®ra, a Daniel…®n akuraz…®
\q2 laionba a gas…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®.вАЭ
\b
\p 
\v 28 Ez…® Darius atrivim…®n ikia ghua g…®n Persian Atrivim Sairus uaghan atrivim…®n itima, Daniel dughiar ruarim…®n gumazir dapanim…®n iti. Egha uaghan gumazir bar ekiam…®n iti.
\c 7
\ms1 Daniel uan irebabagh eghari
\mr (Sapta 7--12)
\s1 Daniel 4plan as…®zibar irebam…®n gani
\p 
\v 1 Dughiar Belsasar Babilon…®n kantrin atrivim itima, an azenir farazim…®n, k…® Daniel, k…® d…®magarir mam…®n dakozim gir…®ghav ikia irebam…®n m…®n bizim…®n gani. Egha k…® irebar kam…®n eghaghanim ak…®nafarir mam…®n an osiri.
\p 
\v 2 Kar bizir k…® d…®magarim…®n irebam…®n ganiziba. Am…®nim danganiba bar dar iza ongarim gamima a d…®kafi, egha d…®p…®ra tintinibar zui.
\v 3 \x - \xo 7:3 \xt Akar Mogomem 13:1; 17:8\x*Ez…® 4plan as…®zir dafar vaghvagha igharagha gariba, ongarim ategha azenan izi.
\p 
\v 4 \x - \xo 7:4-6 \xt Akar Mogomem 13:2\x*Ez…® farazim laion…®n m…®n gara, av…®zimning ikia taragiar ekiam…®n m…®n gari. K…® garav…®ra itima me an av…®zimning asigha an suemning asaraz…® a gumazim m…®n tughav iti. Ez…® me gumazibar n…®ghn…®zim a gan…®ngi.
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® k…® garima naba 2…®n as…®zim, a bean m…®rara gara uan suemning…®n tu. Egha an as…®zir mam…®n iviragharir 3pla uan akam…®n da isaghv…®ra, ez…® tiarir mam a m…®g…®a ghaze, вАЬAria, n…® as…®zir tuzir av…®ribar am…®!вАЭ
\p 
\v 6 Egha k…® garav…®ra itima as…®zir atiar kaziam…®n m…®n gari, ez…® me a d…®bora ghaze lepat, an oto. An ak…®ragharim av…®zir 4pla an iti. Da kuarazir av…®zibar m…®n gara, dapanir 4pla iti. Egha me bizibagh ativagh dar ganamin gavgavim a gan…®ngi.
\p 
\v 7 \x - \xo 7:7 \xt Akar Mogomem 12:3; 13:1\x*Egha k…® garav…®ra itima, namba 4…®n as…®zir bar dafam oto. An guam bar igharagha gari, egha gavgavir ekiam iti. Ez…® k…® bar puv…®ram an atiatingi. An ain…®n atarir bar ekiaba ikiava, biziba bar da apava da orovorogha dagh as…®ghas…®si. Egha g…®n m…®nezir ireziba d…®kava da m…®saraghar…®si. As…®zir kam 10plan komba an dapanim…®n iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a 3plan as…®zir faragha otivizibar m…®n garir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 7:8 \xt Akar Mogomem 13:5-6\x*Egha k…® m…®gh…®gha 10plan kom kabar gara, kom…®n dozir mam…®n garima a mabar tong…®n oto. Ez…® kom…®n igiar kam 3plan kom…®n faragha itiba asi. Ez…® kom…®n igiar kam gumazim…®n damazimning ko akam iti. Egha bar akongegha, uab…® uan ziam fe.
\s1 Daniel irebam…®n garima, Fom…®ra Fom…®ra Itir Gumazim iti
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 7:9 \xt Akar Mogomem 1:14; 20:4\x*Ez…® k…® irebam…®n garima me atrivir dabirabiba inigha iza dar afi. Ez…® Fom…®ra Fom…®ra Itir Gumazir mam iza atrivir dabirabir mam gaperaghav iti. Egha an korotiaba ghuariam…®n m…®n bar ghurghuriz…®, an dapanir ar…®ziba sipsip…®n ar…®zibar m…®n bar ghurghuri. Ez…® atrivir dabirabir kam, wilba iti, egha dabirabim ko an wilba, avir m…®zariaba dar ikiava anek…®arugha anevara.\f + \fr 7:9 \ft Vez…®n kam…®n akar kam, вАЬFom…®ra Fom…®ra Itir Gumazim,вАЭ a God…®n gun m…®gei.\f*
\v 10 \x - \xo 7:10 \xt Akar Mogomem 5:11; 20:12\x*Ez…® avivzariaba dabirabim…®n otivaghira bar ekevegha d…®pam…®n m…®n buigha izaghira tintinibar zui. Ez…® tausen tausen…®n gumazamiziba Gumazir Kam bagha ingari, ez…® milion…®n gumazamiziba an damazim…®n tuivighav iti. Egha marazi kotiabar amuasa ak…®nafariba tui.
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® k…® garav…®ra ikia orazima, namba 4…®n as…®zim…®n kom…®n dozir kam uab…® uan ziam fav…®ra iti. Egha k…® garima me namba 4…®n as…®zir kam m…®suegha an kuam inigha ghua avim m…®k…®niz…® a bar isi.
\v 12 Ez…® 3plan as…®zir ikiav…®ra itir kaba, me dar gavgaviba ag…®fa, eght…® da ua bizibagh ativagh dar ganan kogham. Egha me zuam…®ra dav soghez…® da ariaghirezir puvat…®. Me da ataghiz…®ma da dughiar bar otevim…®n ike.
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 7:13 \xt Matyu 24:30; 26:64; Mak 13:26; 14:62; Luk 21:27; Akar Mogomem 1:7; 1:13; 14:14\x*Ez…® nan irebar k…® d…®magarim…®n ganizir kam, k…® gumazir mam, a Gumazamizibar Otarim…®n m…®n k…® an gani. A ghuariam…®n tong…®n ikegha nan borogh…®n izi. Ez…® me a inigha ghua Fom…®ra Fom…®ra Itir Gumazir Kam gan…®ngi.\f + \fr 7:13 \ft Aram…®n akam…®n ziar kam, вАЬGumazamizibar Otarim,вАЭ Iesus uab…® d…®bori mok…®n.\f*
\v 14 \x - \xo 7:14 \xt Akar Mogomem 11:15\x*Ez…® Fom…®ra Fom…®ra Itir Gumazir Kam uab…® a gamiz…® an atrivim…®n otoz…®, a gavgavim ko ziar ekiam a gan…®ngi. Eght…® ana atrivim…®n ik…®t…®, an gavgavim mamagh…®ra ikiam. Eght…® an atrivir ingangarim g…®vaghan kogham. Eght…® nguibaba bar dar gumazamiziba, ko kantriba bar dar gumazamiziba ko nguibabar akaba bar, me bar an apengan ik…® a bagh ingaram.
\s1 Irebar kam…®n m…®ngarim
\p 
\v 15 Ez…® k…® Daniel, k…® bizir kaba irebam…®n dar ganigha d…®gavir kuram gamigha n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh ami.
\v 16 Egha k…® gumazir kabar mav bagha ghu, an atrivir dabirabim…®n borogh…®ra tughav iti, ez…® k…® uan irebam…®n gun m…®k…®masa an azangs…®si. Ez…® an an m…®ngarim…®n gun na m…®gei.
\v 17 A ghaze, вАЬAs…®zir 4plan ekiar kaba, da kantrin gavgavir 4plan ababanim, da nguazir kam…®n otivam.
\v 18 \x - \xo 7:18 \xt Akar Mogomem 22:5\x*Eght…® g…®n God…®n Bar P…®n Itim…®n gumazamiziba, me gavgavim inigh…®va, biziba bar dagh ativagh, ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam.вАЭ
\p 
\v 19 Ez…® k…® akar kam baregha g…®vagha, namba 4…®n as…®zir kam bar a g…®foghasa. A mabar m…®n garir puvat…®, ez…® k…® bar ana atiatingi. A bizir av…®riba uan bras…®n dagarir puzibar da isa, da apava ain…®n ataribar da orovorogha dagh as…®ghas…®si. Egha g…®n m…®nezir ireziba d…®kava da m…®saraghar…®si.
\v 20 Ez…® k…® uaghan, 10plan kom…®n an dapanim…®n itiba ko kom…®n dozir g…®n otozim, k…® dagh foghasa. Egha kom…®n dozir kam a 3plan kom…®n faragha itiba asiz…® da ire. Ez…® a damazimning ikia, akam ikia, egha akam arava uab…® uan ziam fe. Egha k…® kom…®n dozir kam…®n gara, k…® bar atiatingi. K…® komba bar dar atiatiava, egha dozir kam k…® bar an atiatingi.
\v 21-22 \x - \xo 7:21-22 \xt Akar Mogomem 13:7; Akar Mogomem 20:4\x*Ez…® irebar kam k…® an garima, kom…®n kam God…®n gumazamiziba ko m…®sogha ikia, me d…®kab…®ra ghuavti Fom…®ra Fom…®ra Itir Gumazim oto. Egha a kom…®n kam isa kotiam gat…®gha kamagh…®n m…®gei, God…®n Bar P…®n Itim…®n gumazamiziba, me kotiam…®n aven kom…®n kam gafira. Ez…® dughiam otoz…®ma God…®n gumazamiziba, me biziba bar dagh ativamin gavgavim ini.\f + \fr 7:21-22 \ft Akar kam, Aram…®n akam, deragha an m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®. Gumazir maba ghaze, akar kam kamak…®n, вАЬGumazim ghaze, God…®n Bar P…®n Itim…®n gumazamiziba me gumazir igharazibagh afira.вАЭ Ez…® gumazir maba ghaze, akar kam kamak…®n, вАЬGumazir God…®n Bar P…®n Itim…®n gumazamiziba gavgavim me gan…®dim, a kotiam gatifa.вАЭ\f*
\p 
\v 23 Ez…® gumazir k…® azarazir kam, a kamagh…®n na m…®keme, вАЬIrebar kam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n, namba 4…®n as…®zir kam, a namba 4…®n kantrin ababanim gami. Egh a kantrin igharazibar m…®n ganan kogham. A kantrin igharaziba bar dagh as…®ghas…®gh da d…®kab…®ragh egh da g…®vagham.
\v 24 \x - \xo 7:24 \xt Akar Mogomem 17:12\x*Ez…® 10plan kom…®n kaba, da 10plan atrivibar ababanim, me kantrin kam…®n otivam. Eght…® g…®n atrivir igharazitam otogham, egh an atrivir faragha itibar m…®n ganan kogham. An atrivir 3pla batuegham.
\v 25 \x - \xo 7:25 \xt Akar Mogomem 12:14; 13:5-6\x*Eght…® an akar kurabar God…®n Bar P…®n Itim m…®k…®m…®va, egh an gumazamiziba d…®kab…®nam. Egh me Arazir God Me Gan…®ngiziba ko, dughiar ekiar God…®n ziam feba, da batoghs…® damuam. Egh an azenir pumuning ko m…®kezim ko akuam…®n God…®n gumazamizibagh ativagh men ganam.\f + \fr 7:25 \ft Aram…®n akam deragha vez…®n kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®. Marazi ghaze, an azenir pumuning ko m…®kezim ko akuam m…®gei. Ez…® marazi ghaze, akar kam, a guizbang…®ra, akar mogomem, egha an os…®mt…®zim kam g…®vaghamin dughiam deragha an gun m…®geir puvat…®.\f*
\p 
\v 26 вАЬEght…® an dughiar kam g…®vaght…®, God…®n kotiam otivam, eght…® ana atrivir kam…®n gavgavim ag…®va, egh bar a gas…®ghasigham.
\v 27 \x - \xo 7:27 \xt Akar Mogomem 20:4; 22:5\x*Egh God…®n Bar P…®n Itim, a nguazim…®n atriviba bar dar gavgaviba is…® uan gumazamizibar an…®ngam. Eght…® me atrivibar ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam. Eght…® kantriba bar God…®n gumazamizibar apengan ik…®va, egh ingar…®va men akaba baragham.вАЭ
\p 
\v 28 Kar irebar k…® ganizim…®n eghaghanim, a kamagh…®ra tu. Ez…® k…® Daniel, k…® bar atiatingi, egha atiatir guam asara, egha k…® bizir kaba puv…®ram a dagh n…®ghn…®si.\f + \fr 7:28 \ft Aram…®n akam kagh g…®fa. Me akar sapta 8…®n ikegha ghua 12…®n tuziba, Hibrun akam…®n an osiri.\f*
\c 8
\s1 Daniel irebam…®n sipsip…®n mam ko memen mam…®n gari
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® 3plan azeniba Belsasar atrivim…®n itima, k…® bizir igharazir mam irebam…®n m…®n an gani.
\v 2 K…® irebam…®n uab…®n garima, k…® zuam…®ra ghua Elam…®n provins…®n oto. Egha Susan nguibar ekiam…®n tughav iti. Ulain Fanem…®n borogh…®n.
\v 3 Egha k…® garima sipsip…®n apurir mam fanem…®n borogh…®n tughav iti. Egha kom…®n pumuning iti. Ez…® an komning ruara, ez…® kom…®n mam farazim…®n g…®n otogha bar ruara.
\v 4 Ez…® k…® sipsip…®n apurir kam…®n garima, ana aviragha ivegha ghua aruem uaghiri nagh…®n, ko not ko saut…®n ghu. Eght…® as…®zitam an t…®vaghan kogham. Eght…® tav an gavgavim…®n ar…®mang…®ghan kogham. A biziba uan ifongiam…®n dagh amua egha bar gavgavigha uan ziam fe.
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® k…® bizir kam…®n m…®ngarim n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribar a gamuav…®ra ikia, egha memen apurir mam…®n garima, an aruem ghuaghiri danganim ategha izi. A bar puv…®ra ivemara an sueba nguazim d…®tir puvat…®. Ez…® kom…®n bar ekiar vam…®ra an damazimning…®n tizim…®n tughav iti.
\v 6 Ez…® kom…®n pumuning itir sipsip…®n Fanem…®n borogh…®ra tughav itir k…® ganizim, memen kam an ganigha puv ivegha atarav…®ra sipsip…®n kam bagha ghu.
\v 7 Egha k…® an garima a sipsip m…®sosi. Ez…® memen kam bar an…®ngaghegha, gavgavim uab…®n akuigha ivegha ghua, sipsip…®n apurim uab…® a gasegha an komning ap…®riaghat…®. Sipsip…®n apurim a munasan gavgaviba puvat…®, ez…® meme anekuniz…® a nguazim giraghuz…®, ana d…®kab…®ni. Ez…® sipsip…®n kam…®n akurvaghamin bizitam itir puvat…®.
\v 8 Egha memen kam bar puv…®ra ifaghata, uan gavgavim akakasi. Egha an gavgavim bar ekevezir dughiam…®n, an kom…®n ekiam d…®p…®ri. Ez…® an danganim…®n 4plan kom…®n igharaziba otifi. Egha da bar ekefe. Ez…® kom…®n 4plan kaba nguazim…®n 4plan ruaghateviba bar dar gari.
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® kom…®n dozir igiar mam, 4plan kom…®n kabar mam gis…®n aghui. Egha kom…®n igiar kam…®n gavgavim bar ekefegha ghuav…®ra ikia gumazamizir saut…®n amadaghan itiba ko, aruem anadi nagh…®n itiba ko, God uan gumazamizibagh an…®ngizir nguazir aghuir kam…®n me d…®kab…®ra.
\v 10 \x - \xo 8:10 \xt Akar Mogomem 12:4\x*Ez…® kom…®n kam bar gavgavigha m…®kovezibav sosi. M…®koveziba God…®n Nguibam…®n itir m…®dorozir enselbar m…®n m…®sosi. Ez…® kom…®n kam m…®kovezir maba kuniz…® da nguazim giraghue, ez…® a me d…®kab…®ni.
\v 11 Egha kom…®n kam uaghan God…®n Nguibam…®n m…®dorozir gumazibar atrivim d…®kab…®nasa. An atrivim bagha zurara ofa gamir arazim ag…®vagha, God…®n D…®penim gas…®ghas…®gha a gamima a bar m…®ze.
\v 12 Gumazamiziba arazir kurabagh ami, kamagh…®n kom…®n kam gavgavim inigha God…®n Nguibam…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba me d…®kab…®nasa, egh dughiabar zurara ofa gamir arazim ag…®vasa.\f + \fr 8:12 \ft Hibrun akam deragha vez…®n kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* Ez…® God…®n akaba bar guizbang…®ra, ez…® kom…®n kam God…®n guiz…®n akam gas…®ghas…®ki. Ez…® gumazamiziba uam an g…®n zuir puvat…®. Ez…® biziba bar kom…®n kam dar amuasa, a pura dagh ami.
\p 
\v 13 Egha k…® ensel…®n mam barazima a m…®geima ensel…®n igharazir mam kamagh…®n an azai, вАЬBizir kurar e irebam…®n garir kaba, da dazogh…®n g…®vagham? Gumazamiziba dazogh…®n ua God…®n ofa damuam. God bar aghuazir bizim an D…®penim…®n iti, kamagh…®n a uan D…®penim ataki, eght…® dughiar manam…®n arazir kurar kam g…®vagham? Eght…® dughiar manam…®n kom…®n kam…®n gavgavim g…®vagham? Eght…® a ua God…®n D…®penim gas…®ghas…®ghan kogh…®va, God…®n Nguibam…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba uan suemning…®n me d…®kab…®nan kogham?вАЭ
\p 
\v 14 Ez…® k…® orazima ensel…®n igharazim a ikaragha, kamagh…®n m…®gei, вАЬFom…®ra me m…®zaraziba ko guarat…®zibar ofa God gan…®di. Eght…® bizir kurar kam itir dughiam…®n, me 2,300plan ofaba God dan…®ngan kogham.\f + \fr 8:14 \ft Hibrun akam, d…®bobonir kam iti, 2,300…®n arueba. Me vaghvagh arueba mengt…®, da 2,300plan arueba. Egh me zurara m…®zaraziba ko guarat…®zibar ofa gamir dughiaba mengt…®, da 1,150plan aruebar tugham.\f* Dughiar kam g…®vaght…®, me God…®n D…®penim ak…®riva, ua God…®n ofa damuam.вАЭ
\p 
\v 15 Ez…® k…® Daniel, k…® irebar kam…®n garav…®ra ikia, egha k…® an m…®ngarim g…®foghasa puv…®ra n…®ghn…®si. Egha k…® garima gumazir mam zuam…®ra nan borogh…®n tughav iti.\f + \fr 8:15 \ft Gumazir kam, ensel Gebrielra. (N…® ves 16 ko 17…®n gan.) Ez…® Daniel ghaze, a gumazir mam…®n m…®n an gani.\f*
\s1 Ensel Gebriel irebam…®n m…®ngarim…®n gun m…®gei
\p 
\v 16 \x - \xo 8:16 \xt Luk 1:19; 1:26\x*Ez…® k…® gumazir mam…®n tiarim barazi a Ulain Fanem…®n ikia dia egha kamagh…®n m…®gei, вАЬEnsel Gebriel, n…® bizir Daniel ganizir kam…®n m…®ngarim…®n gun m…®k…®m.вАЭ
\p 
\v 17 Ez…® Gebriel iza nan borogh…®n tuz…®, k…® bar atiatigha, nguazim gir…®gha fuaghav iti. Ez…® Gebriel kamagh…®n na m…®gei, вАЬN…® pura nguazim…®n gumazim, ez…® k…® kamaghsua, n…® irebar kam…®n m…®ngarim g…®fogh. Irebar kam, nguazim g…®vaghamin bizibar m…®g…®r…®g…®am an ti.вАЭ
\p 
\v 18 A m…®g…®av…®ra itima, nan damaziba nan siriz…®, k…® ira m…®togha akuava ongani. Ez…® a nan suiragha na fez…® k…® tu.
\p 
\v 19 Ez…® a m…®gei, вАЬK…® God…®n an…®ngagharim g…®vaghamim dughiam…®n, n…® m…®k…®masa. Kar God inabazir dughiar abuananam. Bizir kaba n…® irebam…®n ganiz…® mogh…®n otivam.
\p 
\v 20 вАЬSipsip…®n apurir kom…®n pumuning itir n…® ganizim, a kantri Midia ko kantri Persian ababanim.
\v 21 Ez…® memen apurir n…® ganizim, a kantri Grik…®n ababanim. Egha an damazimning…®n tong…®n tughav tir kom…®n ekiar kam, a kantri Grik…®n faragha itir atrivim…®n ababanim.
\v 22 Ez…® n…® ganizir kom…®n ekiar d…®p…®rizir kam, 4pla kom…®n maba an danganim otifi. Bizir kam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n. Kantri Grik bigh kantrin igiar 4pla ikiam. Egh me gavgaviba puvat…®gham, mati fom…®ra kantri b…®ghizir puvat…®z…® mok…®n.
\p 
\v 23 вАЬEz…® kantrin kabar gavgavim gevir dughiam…®n, gumazamizibar arazir kuraba bar pazav otoght…®, dughiar kamra, atrivir tam otogham. A bar gumazir kuram. Egh an akaba batogh…®va, navim gavgavigh ifavaribar amuam.
\v 24 An otogh gavgavigh ikiam, ez…® kar guizbang…®ra an gavgavim puvat…®. Eght…® a bizir av…®rim gas…®ghas…®gh…®va, biziba bar dar amus…® n…®ghn…®gh, a pura dar amuam. A gumazir gavgaviba itibagh as…®ghas…®gh, egh God…®n gumazamizibagh as…®ghas…®gham.
\v 25 Egh a gumazamizibagh ifaramin fofozir aghuim ik…®va, egh an ifavarir arazir kam…®n an afiragh bar p…®n ikiam. Egh a uan navir averiam…®n n…®ghn…®gh suam a bar ekefe. Eght…® gumazamiziba suam me derav…®ra iti. Puvat…®, a zuam…®ra d…®kavigh…®va men av…®ribagh as…®ghasigham. Egh a d…®kavigh Atrivir Atriviba Bar Dagh Afirazir Kam m…®soghs…® damuam. Eght…® dughiar kam…®n gumazitam a gas…®ghasighan kogham, a uab…® kuram iniam.вАЭ
\p 
\v 26 K…® guarat…®ziba ko m…®zarazibar ofabagh amir arazim, k…® an irebar m…®ngarim…®n gun n…® m…®keme. Ez…® bizir n…® ganiziba da otivam. Egh bizir kaba zuam…®ram otivighan kogham, kamagh…®n n…® irebar kam…®n akar mogomer kam…®n gun gumazamizibav k…®man mark…®.
\p 
\v 27 Ez…® k…® akar kam baregha g…®vagha, bar oseme, egha dughiar mabar k…® arei. Ez…® ar…®mariam g…®vaz…®ma, k…® d…®kavigha ua ingangarir Atrivim Belsasar na gan…®ngizim bagha ghu. Egha k…® irebar kam puv a g…®n…®ghn…®gha, n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh amua deragha an m…®ngarim g…®fozir puvat…®.
\c 9
\s1 Daniel Israelia bagha God ko m…®gei
\p 
\v 1 Darius, Serksis…®n otarim, a kantri Midian gumazim, egha a kantri Babilon…®n atrivim…®n iti.
\v 2 \x - \xo 9:2 \xt Jeremaia 25:11; 29:10\x*An azenir farazim, ana atrivim…®n itima, k…® Daniel, k…® God…®n ak…®nafariba gara da d…®bori. Egha, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Jeremaia, Ikiav…®ra Itir God a gan…®ngizir akam, k…® a g…®n…®ghn…®si. A ghaze, Jerusalem 70plan azenibar ikuvighv…®ra ikiam.
\v 3 Ez…® k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®gei, Ekiam. Os…®mt…®zim nan navim…®n itima, k…® daghetam apir puvat…®gha, azir akam…®n korotiaba aghuigha, averenim isa uan m…®karzim gaghui. K…® kamagh…®n ikia, egha pamtem God ko m…®gei.
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® k…® Israelian gumazamizibar arazir kurabar gun uan Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n gavgavim m…®gei. K…® kamagh…®n m…®gei, вАЬO God…®n Ekiam, n…® gavgavir ekiam iti, ez…® e n…®n ziam fe. Egha n…® zurara e koma amizir Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n g…®rara zui. Egha n…® zurara gumazamizir n…® gifuegha, n…®n akam…®n g…®n zuiba, n…® bar men apangkufi.
\p 
\v 5 вАЬE gumazamizir derazir puvat…®ziba. E arazir kuram gami, egha n…®n g…®n zuir tuavim ataki. E n…®n akam batuegha, Akar Gavgaviba ko, bizir n…® damuasa e m…®kemeziba e dagh amir puvat…®.
\v 6 N…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba, me n…®n ingangarir gumaziba, e men akam barazir puvat…®. Me n…®n ziam…®n, akam en atrivibav k…®ra, en gumazir dapanibav k…®ra, egha en ovaviba ko en kantrin itir gumazamiziba bar me m…®k…®ni.
\p 
\v 7 вАЬEkiam, n…® arazir aghuibagh amima, ez…® en arazir kuraba aghums…®zir ekiam e gan…®ngi. Ez…® kar bar guizbang…®ra, e Judan nguibam…®n iti, o e Jerusalem…®n iti, o Israelian gumazamizir kantrin rogh…®ra itiba ko saghon itiba bar. Guizbang…®ra, e n…®n akam batoghez…®, kamagh…®n n…® e amadaz…® e tintinibar ghue, ez…® aghums…®zir kam en m…®karzibar ikiav…®ra iti.
\p 
\v 8 вАЬO Ikiav…®ra Itir God, e ko, en atriviba ko en gumazir dapaniba ko en ovaviba, arazir kuraba n…® gamigha aghums…®zir ekiam e gan…®ngi.
\v 9 E n…®n akaba batosi, ez…® n…® Ekiam en God, en apangkuvigha en arazir kuraba g…®n amadi.
\v 10 En Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgavim, e n…®n akam barazir puvat…®. Akar Gavgavir kam, n…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba n…® e m…®k…®masa me m…®keme, ez…® e an g…®n zuir puvat…®.
\v 11 \x - \xo 9:11 \xt Ofa Gami 26:14-39; God…®n Araziba 28:15-68\x*Ez…® e Israelia bar n…®n Akar Gavgaviba abigha, n…®n akam barazir puvat…®. Egha ak…®rim ragha n…®n akam gasara. E arazir kuram n…® gami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® en arazir kuraba tuisigha g…®fa. Egha Akar Gavgavir kam n…® Moses gan…®ngiz…® an an osiri. N…® ivezir kuram gumazamizir ak…®rim ragha n…®n akam gasaraziba me dan…®ngam. N…® ivezir kurar kam e gingegha g…®fa.
\v 12 Egha n…® en gumazir dapaniba ko e damuasa m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, n…® bizir kam gami. Egha n…® Jerusalem puv a gamigha, bar pazav…®ram a gas…®ghas…®ki. Jerusalem gas…®ghas…®zir arazir kam, a nguazim…®n itir nguibar igharazibagh as…®ghas…®zir arazim bar a gafira.
\v 13 Ez…® n…® Moses osirizir akabar aven m…®kemez…® mogh…®n e os…®mt…®ziba isi. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n e uaghan arazir kuram gamir arazim ataghizir puvat…®, egha n…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, n…® e gakongasa e bizitam gamizir puvat…®. Egha e n…®n guiz…®n akam barazir puvat…®.
\v 14 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® en arazir kuraba ikarvaghasa iti. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n n…® a gamigha g…®fa. Guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, n…® arazir aghuibaram ami. Ez…® e n…®n akam barazir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 15 вАЬO Ekiam, en God, n…® uan gavgavim akaghava uan gumazamiziba Isip…®n kalabus…®n me inigha ize. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba, ingangarir n…® amizir kam…®n gavgavim g…®n…®ghn…®ghav…®ra iti. Egha me ziar ekiam n…® gan…®di. Bar guizbang…®ra, e arazir kurar av…®rim gamigha n…®n akam batoke.
\v 16 O Ekiam, n…® en arazir kuraba ko en ovavibar arazir kurabar ganigha, egha puv e gamigha, Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam gas…®ghas…®ki. Ez…® Jerusalem borogh…®ra itir kantribar gumazamiziba, me bar d…®bovir akabar Jerusalem m…®g…®ava, e n…®n gumazamiziba sara m…®gei. E kamaghsua, n…® uam Jerusalem…®n ataran mark…®. Bar guizbang…®ra, kar n…®n nguibam a n…®n m…®ghs…®am gis…®n ti. N…® fom…®ra an ingangarir aghuir av…®rim e bagha dagh ami, ez…® n…® ua kamagh…®n e bagh damuasa e ifonge.
\p 
\v 17 вАЬO en God, nan d…®mdiam ko azangs…®zim barakigh. K…® kamaghsua, n…® uan ziar ekiam g…®n…®ghn…®gh, ua uan D…®penir me as…®ghas…®ghizir kam ak…®righ, eght…® me bar fogh suam, n…® Ekiam.
\v 18 O nan God, en ararem baregh, en gan. N…® os…®mt…®zir kam…®n gari an en ti, ez…® os…®mt…®zim n…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ti. E gumazir aghuibar m…®n n…®n azangs…®ghan kogham. E fo n…®n apangkuvim iti, kamagh…®n e n…®n azangs…®si.
\v 19 O Ekiam, en d…®mdiam baragh! O Ekiam en arazir kuraba g…®n amadagh! O Ekiam, e baragh egh en akuragh! Jerusalem…®n nguibar kam ko an gumazamiziba sara, e n…®n adarazira. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® suighsuighan mark…®. O nan God, n…® uan ziar ekiam g…®n…®ghn…®gh egh zuam…®ra en akuragh!вАЭ
\s1 Ensel Gebriel, Jeremaian akam…®n m…®ngarim…®n gun m…®gei
\p 
\v 20 K…® Daniel, k…® God ko m…®g…®av…®ra iti, egha uan arazir kuraba ko Israelia, me nan gumazamiziba, men arazir kuraba sara, k…® dar gun m…®gei. Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, nan God k…® an azangs…®si, eght…® a uan D…®penim ua m…®ghs…®ar kam gis…®n an ingaright…® a tugham.
\v 21 \x - \xo 9:21 \xt Luk 1:19; 1:26\x*Ez…® k…® God ko m…®g…®av…®ra itima, ensel…®n kam Gebriel, k…® uan irebar farazim…®n an gani, ez…® a dat…®r…®gh…®n m…®ghegha izaghira danganir k…® itim…®n ize. Ez…® dughiar kam, bar guarat…®zim…®n ofa gamir dughiam.
\v 22 Egha a iza kamagh…®n na m…®gei, вАЬDaniel, k…® n…®n n…®ghn…®zim ak…®rasa ize. Eght…® n…® fofozir aghuir av…®riba ikiam.
\v 23 Daniel, n…® God ko m…®geir dughiar kamra, a n…®n azangs…®zim ikaragha g…®fa. God bar n…® gifonge, kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® a n…®n azangs…®zim…®n ikarvazir akam inigha n…® dan…®ngasa izi. Ez…® n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n deraghv…®ram oraght…® k…® akar n…® d…®ponezir kam…®n m…®ngarim…®n gun n…® m…®k…®mam.
\p 
\v 24 вАЬN…® 70plan dughiabar, 7plan azeniba akuvagh kamagh…®ra damu mang…® 490…®n azenibar otogham.\f + \fr 9:24 \ft Daniel 9:24…®n, akar namba 1. God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Jeremaia ghaze, Israel…®n kantri ikuvigh ik…® mang…®t…® 70plan azeniba g…®vagham. Ez…® vez…®n kam…®n, ensel Gebriel kamagh…®n m…®gei, вАЬ70plan azenir kaba,вАЭ da guizbang…®ra 70plan azeniba puvat…®, da 70plan wikba. Gumazir av…®riba ghaze, akar kam, вАЬwikba,вАЭ Hibrun akam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n 7plan azeniba. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, 70plan wikba, kar 70plan azeniba, ez…® n…® 7plan azeniba inigh 70plan dughiabar da akuvaght…®, da bar mogh…®ra 490plan azenibar otogham. Ez…® marazi ghaze, puvat…®, Hibrun akam wikbara m…®gei. Ez…® gumazir maba ghaze, a pura bizir g…®n otivamibar akar is…®n zuibav gei, egha dughiar tam…®n ababanim gamizir puvat…®.\f* Kar dughiar God inabazim, a n…®n gumazamiziba ko n…®n nguibam Jerusalem, a uamategh men arazir kuraba ak…®righ da avegham. A gumazamizibar arazir kuraba bar ada ag…®vaght…®, me arazir aghuim damu mamagh…®ra ikiam. Eght…® God…®n D…®penim uam a baghv…®ra ikiam.\f + \fr 9:24 \ft Daniel 9:24…®n akar namba 2, gumazir maba ghaze, e kamagh…®n akar kam giragham, вАЬA danganir anogoroghezir tam ua baghv…®ra an am…®sevegham.вАЭ Eght…® arazir kam…®n, вАЬGod uab…® gumazitam am…®sevegham, a gumazir bar zuegha arazir aghuibagh amim.вАЭ\f* Eght…® a bizir kabar amut…®, akam inigha izir gumazibar akaba ko irebaba guizbang…®ram otivam.
\p 
\v 25 вАЬN…® oregh…®va, kamagh…®n fogh: Dughiar Jerusalem uam an ingaramin m…®g…®r…®g…®am otogh mang…® 49plan azeniba g…®vaght…®ma, gumazir God en akurvaghasa m…®sevezim, an otogham. Eght…® me ua Jerusalem…®n ingar…®va, nguibar ekiam…®n aven tuavibar ingar…®va, afemozir ekiam gekuight…® a nguibar ekiam…®n d…®vazir gavgavim gighuigham. Eght…® Jerusalem 434plan azenibar kamagh…®ra ikiam, eght…® azenir kaba, kar os…®mt…®ziba ikiamin azeniba.\f + \fr 9:25 \ft Gumazir maba ghaze, e kamagh…®n akar kam giragham, вАЬE kamagh…®n oregh fogham, me ua Jerusalem…®n ingaramin m…®g…®r…®g…®am otoght…®, 7plan dughiabar, 7plan azeniba akuvaghamin dughiam ko 62plan dughiabar, 7plan azeniba akuvaghamin dughiam g…®vaght…®, God m…®seveghamin gumazir ekiar kam otogham. Dughiar kam…®n, me ua Jerusalem…®n ingar…®va, nguibar ekiam…®n aven tuavibar ingar…®va, egh ua afemozir ekiam gekuight…® a nguibar ekiam…®n d…®vazir gavgavim gighuigham. Eght…® azenir kaba, os…®mt…®ziba itir azenibar m…®n ikiam.вАЭ\f*
\v 26 Egh 434plan azeniba g…®vaght…®, me gumazir God en akurvaghasa m…®sevezim m…®sueght…® an aremegham. Eght…® an bizitam ikian kogham.\f + \fr 9:26 \ft Hibrun akam deragha vez…®n kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* Eght…® atrivir gavgavir mam…®n m…®dorozir gumazir b…®zir ekiam iz…®va Jerusalem ko God…®n D…®penim gas…®ghas…®gham. Eght…® dughiar abuananam…®n, mati aperiam faner ekiam…®n otogha, biziba atera zui. Eght…® m…®dorozir ekiam ik…® mang…®t…®, God m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, dughiar abuananam otogham.
\v 27 \x - \xo 9:27 \xt Daniel 11:31; 12:11; Matyu 24:15; Mak 13:14\x*Eght…® atrivir kam gumazamizir av…®rim ko akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavim damuam, eght…® me an akam baragham. Eght…® akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavir kam 7plan azenibar ikiam. Egh mang…® azenir 3pla ko akuam…®n g…®vaght…®, an arazir God…®n ofa gamim ag…®vagham. Eght…® me bizir kurar God bar aghuazim is…® God…®n D…®penim gis…®n anet…®gham, kamagh…®n a uan D…®penim ategham. Eght…® gumazir bizibagh as…®ghas…®zim d…®penir kam…®n ik…® mang…®, God a gas…®ghas…®ghasa inabazir dughiam otogham.вАЭ\f + \fr 9:27 \ft Hibrun akam ves 27…®n akar av…®rim deragha a m…®geir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazir maba akar kam g…®ra arazir igharazibar an osiri.\f*
\c 10
\s1 Daniel Taigris…®n Fanem…®n m…®riam…®n ikiava irebam…®n gani
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Sairus 3plan azenibar kantri Persian atrivim itima, God akam aghurigha Daniel gan…®ngi. Daniel…®n ziar mam Beltesasar. Ez…® akar kam bar guizbang…®ra, egha mong bar p…®n koz…®, an osemegha ghaze, a manmagh…®n a g…®fogham?\f + \fr 10:1 \ft Hibrun akam deragha vez…®n kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* Ez…® God irebam…®n an gun m…®gei.
\p 
\v 2 Ez…® dughiar kabar k…®, Daniel, k…® 3plan wikbar oseme.
\v 3 Egha dagher is…®ngt…®zitam amezir puvat…®gha, as…®zitam ko wain…®n d…®patam nan akatorim giraghuzir puvat…®. Egha boretam uab…® gaghua egha uan dapanir ar…®zim ak…®rizir pu, bar puvat…®, ez…® wigh…®n pumuning ko m…®kezim g…®fa.
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® k…® iak…®nir faragha zuim…®n, an dughiar namba 24…®n, Taigris…®n Faner ekiam…®n m…®riam…®n tughav iti.
\v 5 \x - \xo 10:5-6 \xt Akar Mogomem 1:13-15; 2:18; 19:12\x*Egha uan guam fegha garima, gumazir mam korotiar bar ghurghurim arugha, letiar gol…®n aghuim…®n ingarizim ike.
\v 6 Egha an m…®karzim dag…®ar angazangarim itim…®n m…®n taghtasi. Ez…® an guam mati on…®marim taghtasi. Ez…® an damazimning avim…®n m…®n dafogha isi. Ez…® an aghariba ko sueba da bras…®n m…®n ghurghuriz…®, an tiarim mati gumazir av…®riba m…®gei.
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® k…®, Daniel, k…® uab…®ra irebar kam…®n gani. Ez…® na ko itir darasi, me bizitam…®n ganizir puvat…®gha men m…®karziba pura me d…®kafi. Ez…® me atiatiava ara ghua monge.
\v 8 Ez…® k…® bar uab…®ra ikia d…®gavir kuram gamir irebar kam…®n gani. Egha k…® ua gavgaviba puvat…®z…®, nan guam ovever guam asaragha bar ikufi.
\v 9 Egha k…® an tiarim baregha, egha nguazim gir…®gha akuava onganigha, uan guam nguazim tua.
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® gumazir mam uan dafarim…®n nan suira. Egha na ghufez…® k…® uan dafarimning ko tevir ak…®rimning…®n tu. Egha k…® nuighnuigha irasa amuav…®ra iti.
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® ensel kamagh…®n na m…®gei, вАЬDaniel, God n…® gifonge. Eght…® n…® d…®kavigh bar deraghv…®ra na baraght…®, k…® bizir n…® m…®k…®mamim n…® m…®k…®mam. God uab…® na amadaz…® k…® ize.вАЭ Egha a m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®ma k…® d…®kafi, egha tugha aguav…®ra iti.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 10:12 \xt Daniel 9:3-4; 9:22-23; Aposel 10:4\x*Ez…® a ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, вАЬDaniel, n…® atiatingan mark…®. Dughiar farazimra n…® uab…® d…®kab…®ragha egha an fofozim iniasava ami. Ez…® dughiar kamra, God n…®n d…®mdiam baraki. Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n na amadaz…®, k…® n…®n azangs…®zim bang…®n ize.
\v 13 \x - \xo 10:13 \xt Daniel 10:20-21; 12:1; Jut 1:9; Akar Mogomem 12:7\x*K…® zuam…®ra izasa, ez…® puvat…®. Aser kurar Persian nguibar ekiam gativazim, 21plan dughiabar nan t…®vaz…® k…® ike. Ez…® k…® uab…®ra Persian atriviba ko itima gumazir nan akurvaghamiba puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, enselbar faragha zuir ensel…®n mam, an ziam Maikel, a nan akuraghasa ize.\f + \fr 10:13 \ft Hibrun akam deragha vez…®n kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f*
\v 14 Ez…® k…® bizir g…®n n…®n gumazamiziba bativamim m…®k…®mt…® n…® foghasa ize. N…® irebam…®n m…®n ganizir bizir kam, a bizir g…®n izamibar eghaghanim n…®n aka.вАЭ
\p 
\v 15 Egha a kamagh…®n m…®geima, k…® uan guam nguazim m…®tuagha m…®g…®r…®g…®aba nan puvat…®.
\v 16 Ez…® ensel…®n kam nguazim…®n gumazamiziba en m…®n gari, egha uan dafarim isa nan akam gat…®. Ez…® k…® akam akarigha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, вАЬEkiam, k…® irebar kam…®n ganigha bar atiatigha, puv…®ra n…®gha gavgaviba g…®fa.
\v 17 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar manatam n…® m…®k…®mam? K…® mati ingangarir gumazir uan gumazir ekiam…®n damazim…®n tughav itim. Egha k…® gavgaviba puvat…®gha av…®ghazi.вАЭ
\p 
\v 18 Ez…® ensel…®n kam ua nan suiraz…®, k…® ua gavgafi.
\v 19 \x - \xo 10:19 \xt Gumazir Dapaniba 6:23\x*Egha a kamagh…®n na m…®gei, вАЬGod bar n…® gifonge, ez…® n…® navir am…®rizim…®n ik…®va, atiatingan mark…®. N…® tugh gavgafigh.вАЭ Egha a m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®ma, k…® bar gavgavigha egha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, вАЬGumazir ekiam, n…® gavgavim na ganigha g…®fa, kamagh…®n, n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n bizir kabar gun na m…®k…®m.вАЭ
\p 
\v 20-21 \x - \xo 10:20-21 \xt Akar Mogomem 12:7\x*Ez…® a kamagh…®n na m…®gei, вАЬN…® fo, k…® tizim bagha n…® bagha ize? K…® Guiz…®n Akar Ak…®nafarim…®n aven osirizir, akar mabar gun deraghv…®ra n…® m…®k…®masa ize. Egh k…® dughiar ruarim…®n ikeghan kogham. K…® zuam…®ra uamategh mang…®va, aser kurar Persian kantrin garim ko m…®sogham. Eght…® m…®dorozir kam g…®vaght…®, Grigh…®n kantrin garir aser kuram otogham. Tav nan akurazir puvat…®. Ensel Maikel, a Israelia ian gari, egha a uab…®ra nan akura.вАЭ
\c 11
\nb 
\v 1 Ez…®, azenir faragha zuim…®n Midian kantrin gumazim Darius Babilon…®n kantrin atrivim…®n itima, k…® ensel Maikel…®n akura.
\s1 Isip ko Sirian atrivimning uaning m…®sosi
\p 
\v 2 Ez…® ensel…®n kam ua kamagh…®n na m…®gei, вАЬDaniel, n…® oragh. Bizir k…® n…® m…®k…®mamin kaba, da bar guizbang…®ram otivam. Eght…® atrivir 3pla otogh…®va Persian kantri gativagh an ganam. Eght…® g…®n atrivitam uam otogham. Egh namba 4…®n atrivir kam dag…®ar av…®riba ko bizir av…®riba ik…®va, kantri Persian atrivir maba bar dagh afiragham. Eght…® an gavgavim bar ekeveght…®, a bizir av…®rim ikiam, egh a kantriba bar dar amut…® men naviba bar ikuvight…® me kantri Grik ko m…®soghs…® damuam.
\v 3 Eght…® g…®n atrivir gavgavitam otogh, egh kantrin av…®riba ko gumazamizir av…®ribagh ativagham. Egh bizir manam ana damus…®, ana damuam.
\v 4 Eght…® an gavgavim ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…®, an kantri bigh, 4plan kantribar otivight…®, an boribara kantrin kabagh ativagh dar ganan kogham. Puvat…®. Gumazir igharaziba dagh ativagham, eght…® dar gavgavim atrivir kam…®n gavgavim…®n m…®n gavgavighan kogham.
\p 
\v 5 вАЬEght…® dughiar kam…®n, Isip…®n atrivim,\f + \fr 11:5 \ft Hibrun akam…®n me deragha kantrin kamning, Isip ko Siria, aning…®n ziamning deragha aning d…®borir puvat…®. Me ghaze, вАЬNot…®n amadaghan itir kantri,вАЭ egha вАЬSaut…®n amadaghan itir kantri.вАЭ Ez…® sapta 11…®n vez…®n av…®riba, e dar gara ghaze, вАЬNot…®n amadaghan itir kantri,вАЭ a guizbang…®ra Sirian kantri m…®gei. Ez…® вАЬSaut…®n amadaghan itir kantri,вАЭ a Isip…®n kantri m…®gei. Ez…® sapta 11…®n vez…®n abuananam, marazi ghaze, akar kam ua Isip ko Siria m…®geir puvat…®. Me ghaze, a kantrin igharazibav gei.\f* gavgavim ikiam. Eght…® an gumazir dapanir mam kantrin igharazim…®n atrivim…®n ikiam. Egh an gavgavim bar ekeveght…®, a Isip…®n atrivim…®n gavgavim gafiragham. Eght…® kantrin a ganamin kam, a bar ekevegh kantrin igharazibagh afiragham.
\v 6 Eght…® azenir mabar g…®n Isip…®n atrivim uan borir guivim amadaght…® a mang…® Sirian kantrin atrivim…®n amuim…®n ikiam. Arazir kam kantrining damight…® aning uaning inigh deraghv…®ra ikiam. Eght…® amizir kam…®n gavgavim dughiar ruarim…®n ikeghan koght…®, an pam…®n gavgavim g…®vagham. Eght…® me amizir kam ko, an borim ko, a ko ghuezir darazi ko, an pam, me me m…®sueght…® me aremegham.\f + \fr 11:6 \ft Hibrun akam deragha vez…®n kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®. Marazi ghaze, vez…®n kam an amizir kam…®n borim m…®gei, egha an afeziam m…®geir puvat…®.\f*
\p 
\v 7 вАЬEght…® g…®n amizir kam…®n anabatam Isip…®n atrivim…®n otogham. Egh atrivir kam Sirian atrivim…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba ko m…®sogh, egh nguibar ekiam…®n d…®vazir gavgavim…®n aven mang…®, m…®sogh…®va me kuavaremegham.
\v 8 Egh a men asebar marvir guaba, ko men aseba baghav…®ra itir bizir aghuir me silva ko gol…®n ingariziba, ko bizir aghuir igharaziba sara, inigh Isip…®n mangam. Eght…® bizir kabar g…®n azenir tabar m…®doroziba puvat…®gham.
\v 9 Eght…® g…®n Sirian atrivim Isip…®n mang…® egh Isip ko m…®sogham. Egh m…®dorozim ategh, ua uan kantrin mangam.
\p 
\v 10 вАЬSirian atrivim…®n otariba, m…®dorozir gumazir av…®riba inigh me akuvagh m…®dorozim bagh ikiam. Eght…® atrivim…®n otaritam, m…®dorozir gumazir kaba inigh zuam…®ra mang…® aperiam…®n m…®n men nguibaba avaragham. Egh me nguibar d…®vazir gavgavim itim ko m…®sogham, kar nguibar Isip…®n atrivim ativazim.
\p 
\v 11 вАЬEght…® Isip…®n atrivim adarir ekiam ik…® mang…® Sirian atrivim ko m…®sogh, egh an m…®dorozir gumazir av…®rim d…®kab…®ragh kalabus dat…®gham.
\v 12 Egh a m…®dorozir kam d…®kab…®ragh, egh kamagh…®n a bar akuegh uan ziam fam. A tausenplan m…®dorozir gumazir av…®rim m…®sueght…® me ar…®ghiregham, eght…® an gavgavim dughiar ruarim…®n ikian kogham.
\p 
\v 13 вАЬEgh Sirian atrivim uamategh uan kantri bagh mang…®va m…®dorozir gumazir av…®rim akuvaght…®, men d…®bobonim fom…®ra m…®soghezir m…®dorozir gumazibar d…®bobonim gafiragham. Eght…® azenir g…®n izamim, a uamategh iz…® m…®dorozir gumazir gavgavir av…®rim inigh mang…® Isip…®n atrivim ko m…®sogham. Egh me dagher av…®riba ko bizir av…®riba sara inigh mangam.
\p 
\v 14 вАЬEght…® dughiar kam…®n gumazir av…®rim Isip…®n atrivim…®n apanim…®n ikiam. Ez…® Daniel n…®n adarazir marasi, me an…®ngagharir arazim ik…®, irebam…®n ganigh, bizir kam bagh d…®kavigh m…®soghs…® damuam. Egh me Isip ko m…®sogh, egh me iregham.
\v 15 Eght…® Sirian atrivim uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, me iz…® nguibar gavgavir mam d…®vazim…®n m…®n anerugh nguibam inis…® m…®sogh, egh a d…®kab…®ragham. Eght…® Isip…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba ua m…®soghan kogham. Eght…® men m…®dorozir gumazir gavgavir aghuiba, uaghan m…®soghamin gavgaviba puvat…®gham.
\v 16 Eght…®, Sirian atrivim uan ifongiam…®n bizibar me damuam. Eght…® gumazitam an anogoreghan kogham. Egh a nguazir aghuir God uan gumazamizibagh an…®ngizir kam inigh, egh nguazir kam gas…®ghas…®ghamin gavgavim an dafarim…®n ikiam.
\p 
\v 17 вАЬEgh g…®n Sirian atrivim uam uan m…®dorozir gumaziba bar me inigh, Isip…®n kantri ko m…®soghs…® mang…®s…® n…®ghn…®gham. Egh kantrining uaning inigh deragh ikiasa, a uan guivim amadaght…® a mang…® Isip…®n atrivim…®n amuim…®n ikiam. A ghaze, tuavir kam…®n a Isip…®n nguibam d…®kab…®ragham. Eght…® an n…®ghn…®zir kam guiz…®n otoghan koght…®, a bizitam inighan kogham.\f + \fr 11:17 \ft Hibrun akam deragha vez…®n kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f*
\v 18 Eght…® g…®n a mang…® nguibar ongarim…®n m…®riam…®n itiba ko m…®sogh, egh nguibar av…®riba d…®kab…®ragham. Eght…® kantrin igharazim…®n gumazir dapanim, a Sirian atrivim uab…® fer arazir kuram d…®kab…®ragh, egh an arazir kurar kamra a ikaragh, bar a d…®kab…®ragham.
\v 19 Eght…® Sirian atrivim uamategh uan nguibam…®n mang…®gh, nguibar ekiam…®n d…®vazim…®n ikiam. Egh a ir…®gh bar g…®vaght…®, me uam an ganighan kogham.
\p 
\v 20 вАЬEght…® atrivir igharazitam an danganim inigh, kantrin an ativaziba bizir aghuiba ua bagh da inis…® n…®ghnigh, egh gumazitam amadaght…®, a nguibar bar aghuir kam…®n mang…® me ab…®n men dag…®aba iniam.\f + \fr 11:20 \ft Hibrun akam deragha vez…®n kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®. Gumazir maba ghaze, вАЬnguibar bar aghuir kam,вАЭ a Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam m…®gei. Ez…® marazi ghaze, a God…®n D…®penir Jerusalem…®n itim m…®gei.\f* Egh atrivir kam m…®dorozim…®n aremeghan kogham. Egh uaghan gumazitam an atar a m…®sueght…® an aremeghan kogham. Eght…® atrivir kam bar dughiar otevim…®n ikegh ovengam.вАЭ
\s1 Sirian kantrin itir atrivir kuram
\p 
\v 21 Ez…® ensel ghua kamagh…®n Daniel m…®gei, вАЬEght…® g…®n atrivir tam Sirian kantrin otogh, egh an araziba bar ikuvigham. Gumazir kam, Sirian gumazamizibar ifongiam…®n atrivim…®n otoghan kogham, a uan n…®ghn…®zim…®n atrivim…®n otogham. Egh a zuam…®ra otogh akar asuibav k…®m…®va akar ifavaribar amu, egh Sirian atrivim…®n ikiam.
\v 22 Eght…® m…®dorozir gumazir av…®rim a m…®soghs…® iz…®t…®, a me d…®kab…®ragh bar me a gevegham. Egh uaghan, a God…®n Ofa Gamir Gumazibar Dapanir Ekiam d…®kab…®ragham.\f + \fr 11:22 \ft Gumazir maba ghaze, akar kam ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim…®n m…®geir puvat…®. Me ghaze, gumazir dapanir igharazim atrivim ko akam ak…®ri.\f*
\v 23 An kantri suviz…®, eght…® a kantrin taba ko, akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavir ifavarir tabar amigham, egh m…®k…®m suam a me ko deraghv…®ra ikiam. Egh a zuam…®ra kantrin a m…®soghasa n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®ziba ko m…®sogham. Eght…® arazir kam…®n an gavgavim bar ekevegham.
\v 24 Eght…® kantrin maba navir am…®rizim…®n ik…® m…®soghs…® n…®ghn…®ghan koght…®, a zuam…®ra d…®kavigh pura me ko m…®sogham. Ez…® kantrin kaba, kar kantrin dag…®ar av…®riba itiba. Egh a bizir aghuir a m…®sogha iniziba, a uan roroaba ko da tuiragh me da iniam. Kar an ovaviba fom…®ram amizir puvat…®zir arazim. Egh a nguibar d…®vazir gavgaviba itiba inis…®, ua m…®soghs…® n…®ghn…®gh, egh a men tarazi iniam. Egh a bizir kaba dughiar bar otevimra dar amuam.
\p 
\v 25 вАЬEgh atrivir kam Isip…®n atrivim…®n atiatighan kogham. Egh, a m…®dorozir gumazir av…®rir ekiam akuvagh Isip ko m…®sogham. Eght…® Isip…®n atrivim m…®dorozir gumazir gavgavir taba ua bagh da inigh, egh uaghan Sirian atrivim ko m…®sogham. Eght…® gumazitaba Isip…®n atrivim gifar…®va a damut…® a bar foghan kogh, egh kamagh…®n, a ir…®gham.
\v 26 Isip…®n atrivim…®n gumazir dapanibara pazav…®ra a damigham. Eght…® Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba an m…®dorozir gumazibav sueght…® me bar ar…®ghiregham.
\v 27 Egh g…®n atrivir kamning uaning inigh daperagh damam. Egh aning…®n n…®ghn…®ziba bar ikuvight…®, aning akam git…®va, akar ifavarir av…®ribar uaning m…®k…®mam. Egh bizir aning damuasa ifongeziba, aning dar amighan kogham. God bizir kabar amuasa inabazim dughiam a t…®ghar otivam.
\v 28 Egh Sirian atrivim, bizir a m…®dorozim…®n iniziba, bar da inigh izam, egh a ua uan nguibam…®n mangam. Egh gumazamiziba God…®n ziam fer arazim gas…®ghas…®ghs…® n…®ghn…®zir tam damuam. Ez…® bizir a damuasa ifongeziba, a pura dar amuam. Egh g…®n a uamategh uan nguibam…®n mangam.
\p 
\v 29 вАЬEght…® dughiar God inabazim…®n, Sirian atrivim Isip…®n mang…®gh…®va ua Isip ko m…®sogham, egh a dughiar kam…®n a faragha me m…®sogha me ab…®niz…® mogh…®n, ua kamagh…®n damighan kogham.
\v 30 Eght…® Rom…®n gumazamiziba kuribar iz…®va a m…®sogham, eght…® a bar atiatigham. Egh a bar puv atar…®va uamategh mang…®, gumazamizir God…®n ziam fer arazim gas…®ghas…®ghs…® damuam. Egh a gumazamizir ak…®rim ragha God gasaraziba men m…®g…®r…®g…®aba ko n…®ghn…®zibar g…®n mangam.
\p 
\v 31 \x - \xo 11:31 \xt Daniel 12:11; Matyu 24:15; Mak 13:14\x*вАЬEght…® an m…®dorozir gumaziba otivigh God…®n D…®penim damut…® a God…®n damazim…®n m…®zegham. Egh me Israelian t…®vaght…®, me zurara ofa gamir arazim damuan kogham, egh bizir bar kuratam God…®n D…®penim…®n a damight…® a tugham, kamagh…®n a uan D…®penim ategham.\f + \fr 11:31 \ft Akar kam, вАЬbizir bar kuratam,вАЭ an akar bar faraghav…®ra itim, a Daniel 9:27…®n iti.\f*
\v 32 \x - \xo 11:32 \xt Daniel 11:21; 11:34; Maika 5:7-9; Sekaraia 10:3-6\x*Egh atrivim gumazamizir ak…®rim ragha God gasaraziba, akar bar is…®ngt…®zir aghuibar me m…®k…®mt…®ma, me an g…®n mangam. Eght…® gumazir God…®n apengan itiba, me tuivigh gavgavigh an akaba batogham.
\p 
\v 33 вАЬEght…® Israel…®n gumazir dapanir fofozir aghuiba itiba, me gumazamizibar akurvagh n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba me dan…®ngam. Eght…® men tarazi, apaniba m…®dorozir sababar me m…®soght…® me ar…®m…®ghiram, egh tarazi me me dapongt…® me ar…®m…®ghiram. Egh me gumazir dapanir tabar bizitaba ok…®m…®va me is…® kalabus dar…®gham. Egh me arazir kam dughiar ruarim…®n a damighan kogham.
\v 34 Eght…® dughiar me God…®n gumazir dapanibav soght…® me ar…®m…®ghiramim, gumazitaba men akurvagham. Eght…® men av…®riba uari uarir akurvaghs…® n…®ghn…®gh…®va, men akurvagham.
\v 35 Eght…® apaniba gumazir dapanir tabav soght…® me ar…®ghiram. Eght…® men os…®mt…®zir kam gavgavim gumazamizir mabar an…®ngam. Me arazir aghuibar amuva, God…®n damazim…®n bar zuegham. Eght…® arazir kam g…®vaghan kogham. A kamagh…®ra ik…® mang…® God inabazir dughiar abuananam…®n tugham.
\p 
\v 36 \x - \xo 11:36 \xt 2 Tesalonika 2:3-4; Akar Mogomem 13:5-6\x*вАЬEght…® Sirian atrivir kam uan ifongiam…®n bizibar amuam. Egh a uab…® uan ziam f…®va kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, k…® aseba bar dagh afira. Egh an akar d…®bovibav k…®m…®va, God…®n Bar P…®n Itim…®n ziam d…®kab…®nam. A kamagh…®ra damu mang…®v…®ra ik…® mang…®t…® God…®n an…®ngagharim…®n dughiam otogham. Guizbang…®ra, God uan n…®ghn…®zim…®n g…®n mang…®, biziba bar dar amuam.
\v 37 Eght…® atrivir kam uan ovavibar aseba bar men aghuagh…®va, uaghan amiziba g…®n zuir asem…®n aghuagham. Egha, a uab…® m…®g…®a ghaze, k…® uab…®ra faraghav…®ra ikia dagh afira, egh kamagh…®n, a bar aseba ak…®rim ragh dagh asaragham.\f + \fr 11:37 \ft Hibrun akam deragha vez…®n kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f*
\v 38 Egh an aser vam…®ra ziar ekiam a dan…®ngam. Aser kam, a nguibar ekiar d…®vaziba itibar gari. Ez…® atrivir kam…®n ovaviba aser kam…®n ziam fom…®ram a feir puvat…®. Eght…® atrivim gol ko silva ko dag…®ar bar aghuiba, ko bizir aghuir maba sara aser kam bagh dar an…®ngam.
\v 39 Eght…® a nguibar d…®vazir gavgaviba itibav soghs…® mang…®, egh a uab…®n akurvaghs…® men aser kam…®n azangs…®gham. Egh a gumazir a gifongeziba, a men atrivim…®n ik…®, egh a ziar ekiam me dan…®ng, egh a me damut…® me gumazir dapanibar otivt…®, a nguaziba bizir aghuibar m…®n me dan…®ngam, egh akurvazir me a gamizim ikarvagham.
\p 
\v 40 вАЬEght…® dughiar abuananam rogh…®ra iz…®t…®, Isip…®n atrivim iz…® a ko aning uaning m…®sogham. Eght…® Sirian atrivim karisba ko hoziaba ko kuriba inigh, zuam…®ra mang…® Isip…®n atrivim ko pamtem m…®sogham. Egh kantrin av…®riba aperiar dafam…®n m…®n otogh me arigham.
\v 41 Eght…® m…®dorozir gumazir kaba iz…® God uan gumazamizibagh an…®ngizir nguazir aghuir kam…®n otogham. Egh me tausen tausen…®n gumazamizibav sogh…®rar…®gham. Egh m…®dorozir gumazir kaba kantri Idom ko Moap ko kantri Amon…®n nguazir otevir ekiam inighan kogham.
\v 42 Eght…® atrivir kam nguibar av…®rim d…®kab…®ragh, egh uaghan Isip ateght…® a deraghv…®ra ikian kogham. Puvat…®.
\v 43 Egh a Isip…®n ivezir ekiaba itir bizir aghuir maba ko gol ko silvan av…®rim inigham. Egh kantri Libia ko Itiopia d…®kab…®raght…®, aning an apengan ikiam.
\v 44 Eght…® g…®n gumaziba aruem anadi nagh…®n ko not…®n ikegh iz…®va akar tam a m…®kemeght…®, akar kam a damight…® a d…®gavir kuram damigh bar an…®ngaghegham. Egh a navim bar an ikuvight…®, a pamtem m…®sogh gumazamizir av…®rim kuavaremegham.
\v 45 Egh a ua bagh averpenir ekiaba, nguazir otevir mam…®n dar ingaram, nguazir kam a Mediterenian…®n Ongarir Ekiam…®n m…®riam ko God…®n D…®penim itir m…®ghs…®am…®n t…®zim…®n iti. M…®ghs…®ar kam bar zuegha bar deragha taghtasi, kar God…®n m…®ghs…®am. Eght…® atrivir kam bar g…®vagham, eght…® tav an akuraghan kogham.вАЭ
\c 12
\s1 Dughiar abuananam
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 12:1 \xt Matyu 24:21; Mak 13:19; Akar Mogomem 7:14; 12:7\x*Ez…® ensel…®n korotiar ghurghurim aruzim, kamagh…®n m…®gei, вАЬDughiar kam otivam, ensel…®n bar ekiam Maikel, kar Israel…®n gumazamizibar garir ensel, an otogham. Eght…® dughiar kam…®n os…®mt…®zir bar ekiam otivam. Egha fom…®ra os…®mt…®zir kamagh…®n garitam nguazir kam…®n nguibatam…®n otozir puvat…®. Ez…® dughiar os…®mt…®zir kam otivamim, Israelian gumazamizir men ziaba God…®n ak…®nafarim…®n aven itiba God ua me iniam.
\v 2 \x - \xo 12:2 \xt Aisaia 26:19; Matyu 25:46; Jon 5:29\x*Eght…® God gumazamizir av…®rir ovengeziba ua me f…®t…® me ua d…®kavam. Men marazi zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuim iniam. Eght…® men tarazi bar aghums…®gh…®va kamagh…®ra ik…®v…®ra ikiam.
\v 3 \x - \xo 12:3 \xt Daniel 11:33-35; Matyu 13:43; 1 Korin 15:41-42; Jems 5:20\x*Eght…® gumazir fofozir aghuiba ko n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba itiba, me m…®koveziba isi mogh…®n isi taghtagham. Eght…® gumazir gumazamizir av…®rim arazir aghuibar g…®n mangasa men sure gamiba, me zurara m…®kovezibar m…®n isi taghtagh mamagh…®ra ikiam.
\v 4 \x - \xo 12:4 \xt Akar Mogomem 22:10\x*Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n a na m…®g…®a ghaze, вАШN…® Daniel, n…® akaba itir ak…®nafarir kam dukuagh, egh kendel gris a dat…®ght…®, an akaba modogh ikiam. Egh ak…®nafarir kam dukuagh mamagh…®ra ik…® mang…® dughiar abuananam otogham. Eght…® gumazamizir av…®rim pamtem akar kam…®n m…®ngarim g…®foghs…® damuva avegham.вАЩ вАЭ\f + \fr 12:4 \ft Amos 8:12 vez…®n kam…®n itir akam…®n m…®rara ghu. Ez…® Hibrun akam deragha akar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®. Gumazir av…®rim ghaze an m…®ngarim kamagh…®n ghu, вАЬGumazamizir av…®rim danganiba bar dar aruam, egh bizir guar av…®ribar fofozir av…®riba iniam.вАЭ\f*
\s1 D…®par m…®riam…®n itir enselning…®n irebam
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® k…® Daniel, k…® g…®n garima, gumazir pumuning fanem…®n m…®riamning…®n tughav iti. Mam vong…®n itima, ez…® mam vong…®n iti.
\v 6 Ez…® aning…®n mav, ensel…®n korotiar ghurghurim arugha mong fanem…®n p…®n itim kamagh…®n an azangs…®gha ghaze, вАЬDughiar manamra bizir me gan…®va atiatingamiba g…®vagham?вАЭ
\p 
\v 7 \x - \xo 12:7 \xt Akar Mogomem 10:5; 12:14\x*Ez…® ensel…®n korotiar ghurghurim aruzim, a uan agharimning v…®raram aning ghufegha God…®n Nguibam…®n akui. Egha kamagh…®n m…®gei, вАЬK…® God…®n Mamagh…®ra Itim…®n ziam…®n, bar guizbang…®ra m…®gei. Bizir n…® gan…®va atiatingamiba, azenir pumuning ko m…®kezim ko akuam…®n mang…®va g…®vagham. Eght…® me God…®n gumazamizibar gavgavim d…®kab…®raght…®, eght…® me bar ikuvigha, dughiar kamra bizir kaba uaghan g…®vagham.вАЭ\f + \fr 12:7 \ft Hibrun akam deragha vez…®n kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®. Gumazir maba ghaze, a azenir pumuning ko m…®kezim ko akuam m…®gei. Ez…® gumazir maba ghaze, akar kam, a guizbang…®ra akar mogomem, egha os…®mt…®zir kam g…®vaghamin dughiam deragha a m…®geir puvat…®.\f*
\s1 Enselning…®n irebam…®n m…®ngarim
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® a m…®geima, k…® a baregha, akam…®n m…®ngarim g…®fozir puvat…®. Egha k…® kamagh…®n an azai, вАЬGumazir ekiam, bizir kaba manmagh…®n g…®vagham?вАЭ
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® a kamagh…®n nan akam ikaragha ghaze, вАЬDaniel, n…® mang…®. Guizbang…®ra, ak…®nafarim n…® a dukuagha g…®fa. Eght…® akar kam…®n m…®ngarim modogh mamagh…®ra ik…® mang…® dughiar abuananam otogham.
\v 10 \x - \xo 12:10 \xt Akar Mogomem 22:11\x*Eght…® bizir kaba otiv gumazamizibar amut…® me arazir aghuibar amuam. Egh me God…®n damazim…®n zuegham. Egh gumazamizir fofozir aghuiba ko n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba itir kaba, merara bizir kam…®n m…®ngarim g…®fogham. Eght…® gumazamizir kuraba me bizir kam…®n m…®ngarim g…®foghan kogham. Egh me arazir kurar av…®rim damuam.
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 12:11 \xt Daniel 9:27; 11:31; Matyu 24:15; Mak 13:14\x*вАЬEght…® g…®n apaniba Israelian t…®vaght…® me zurara ofa gamir arazim damuan kogham. Eght…® bizir bar kuratam me God…®n D…®penim…®n aven anesaraght…®, kamagh…®n a uan D…®penim ategham, kar God bar aghuazir bizim. Dughiar kam ik…® mang…®, 1,290plan dughiaba g…®vaght…®ma, bizir kurar kam g…®vagham.
\v 12 Eght…® gumazamizir God bagha tuivigha gavgavigha itiba, a m…®zuam mang…®t…® 1,335plan dughiaba g…®vaght…®, me bar akuegh ikiam.
\p 
\v 13 вАЬEght…® n…®, Daniel, n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n tugh gavgavigh mang…®t…® dughiar abuananam otogham. Eght…® n…® aremegham, egh n…® g…®n ua d…®kavigham, egh dughiar abuananam…®n God n…® bagha inabazir biziba, n…® da iniam.вАЭ
